hadiths[173]{hadithnumber,text}:
3927,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke logon sey jang karun yahan tak key wo ""لَا إِلٰهَ إلاَّ اللہ"" ka iqrar kar lein. jab wo ye kalima padh lein to unhoney apney khoon aur maal mujh sey mehfooz kar liye, siwaye iskey ke us (iqrar, yani kalimey aur Islam) ka koi haq ho (to phir logon key jaan aur maal mein tasarruf karna jayez hoga). aur (dil key maamlat mein) unka hisab Shaan wale Allah key zimmey hai."
3928,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main logon sey jang karun yahan tak key wo لَا إِلٰهَ إلاَّ اللہ keh lein. jab wo لَا إِلٰهَ إلاَّ اللہ keh leingey (uska iqrar kar leingey to unhoney apney khoon aur maal mujh sey mehfooz kar liye) haan (magar is) kalimey (kaa koi haq ho) to phir logon key jaan aur maal mein tasarruf (dakhal) karna jayez hoga. aur unka hisab Allah key zimmey hai."
3929,"Hazrat Aus bin Abu-Aus Huzefa Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas bethey they aur aap hamein waaz aur nasihat farma rahey they ke eik aadmi aaya aur usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey chupkey chupkey baat ki. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey ley jao aur qatl kar do. jab wo aadmi uth kar chala to Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney usey bulaya aur farmaya : kya to gawahi deta hai ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin? usney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : jao usey azad kar do. mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke logon sey jang karun yahan tak key wo لَا إِلٰهَ إلاَّ اللہ ka iqrar kar lein. jab wo aisa karen to un ki janen aur maal mujh par haram hain."
3930,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwaayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nafey bin Azraq aur uskey sathi aaye, unhoney kaha : Imran ! aap halak ho gaey. unhoney farmaya : main halak nahin huwa. unhoney kaha : kyon nahin ! (aap zaroor tabah ho gaey hain). Imran (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main kaisey halak ho gaya? un logon ney kaha ke Allah Taala ney farmaya : ( وَ قَاتِلُوْهُمْ حَتّٰی لَا تَكُوْنَ فِتْنَةٌ وَّ یَكُوْنَ الدِّیْنُ كُلُّهُ لِلّٰهِ ),''un sey jang karo yahan tak key fitna baqi na rahey aur mukammal tor par Allah ka Deen ghalib ho jaey.'' unhoney farmaya : hamney un (kuffar) sey jang ki yahan tak key unhen mulk (Arab) sey nikal diya aur Allah ka Deen mukammal taur par ghalib ho gaya. agar tum chaho to tumhen eik hadees sunaun jo mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suni hai. unhoney kaha : aap ney khud Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suni hai? farmaya : haan, main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas mojud tha (jab aap ney ye farmaya), Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mushrekin sey jang karney key liye musalmanon ka eik lashkar rawana farmaya. jab un (musalmanon) ka un (mushrikon) sey samna huwa to un sey shadeed jang hui. aakhir wo log musalmanon sey maghloob (parajit) ho gaey. merey rishtey-daaron mein sey eik aadmi ney eik mushrik par neze sey hamla kiya. jab wo uskey sar par pahunch gaya to (dushman fauj key) us shakhs ney kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin. main musalman hun. us (Sahabi) ney (uskey kalima shahadat par yaqin na kartey huye) usey neza maar kar qatl kar diya. phir wo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur kaha : Allah key Rasool ! main tabah ho gaya. aap ney eik baar ya do baar farmaya : tu ney kya kiya hai? usney jo kiya tha bata diya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey farmaya : tu ney uska pet kyon na cheer liya ke tujhey malum ho jata ke uskey dil mein kya hai? usney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! agar main uska pet cheerta to kya mujhey malum ho jata ke uskey dil mein kya hai? aap ney farmaya : phir tu ney na to uski zaban key alfaz ko qubul kiya, na to uskey dil ki kaifiyat sey waqif hai. Raavi bayan kartey hain : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khamosh ho gaey (uska uzr qubul nahin farmaya). kuch arsa baad wo faut ho gaya, hamney usey dafn kiya. subah hui to wo zamin ki satah par tha. logon ney kaha : shayad kisi dushman ney isey qabr sey khod nikala hai. phir hamney isey dafn kiya aur apney ladkon ko hukm diya ke uska pehra den. (iskey bawajood) wo (uski laash) subah ko (qabr sey bahir) zamin par (padi) thi. hamney kaha : shayad ladkon ko ungh aa gaee  (un ki ghaflat sey faeyda utha kar kisi ney maiyat nikal li). hamney isey (phir) dafn kiya aur khud pehra diya. (iskey bawajood) subah ko uski laash (qabr sey bahir) zamin par thi, chunanche hamney isey kisi ghaati mein phenk diya (aur dafn na kiya). Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey (eik) riwayat (is tarah) hai, unhoney farmaya : hamein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik jangi muhim par rawana farmaya. eik musalman ney eik mushrik par hamla kiya. aur aakhir tak waqiyaa bayan farmaya. uskey aakhir mein ye izafa hai : usey zamin ney bahar nikal diya, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khabar di gaee to aap ney farmaya : zamin us ko bhi qubul kar leti hai jo us sey ziyada bura hota hai lekin Allah ney tumhen ye dikhaana chah hai ke لَا إِلٰهَ إلاَّ اللہ ka ehtiraam kitna azeem (aur ahmiyat ka hamil) hai."
3931,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hajjatul-wadaa mein farmaya : suno ! sab sey ziyada ehtiraam wala din tumhara ye din hai. suno ! sab sey ziyada ehtiraam wala mahina tumhara ye mahina hai. suno ! sab sey ziyada ehtiraam wala shehar tumhara ye shehar hai. suno ! tumharey khoon aur tumharey maal tumharey liye (eik doosrey key liye) isi tarah qaabil ehtiraam hain jis tarah tumharey is shehar mein is mahiney mein ye din. suno ! kya mainey (Allah ka hukm haq ke mutabiq pahuncha diya hai? haazirin ney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : ya Allah ! gawah reh."
3932,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Kaba Shareef ka tawaf kartey dekha. aap farma rahey they : to kitna pakizah hai ! aur teri khushbu kitni pakizah hai ! to kis qadr azeem hai ! tera ehtiraam kitna azeem hai ! qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki jaan hai ! Allah key yahan momin ki hurmat teri hurmat sey badh kar hai, yani uskey maal aur jaan ki hurmat, aur ye ke uskey barey mein bad-gumaani karna bhi haram hai."
3933,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har musalman doosrey key liye qabile-ehtiraam hai, yani uski jaan, uska maal aur uski aabroo."
3934,"Hazrat Fazala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : momin wo hai jis sey logon ko apney maalon aur apni janon key barey mein khatra na ho, aur Muhajir wo hai jo ghaltiyaan aur gunah tarak kar dey."
3935,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney sare-aam (kisi ka maal waghera) chhina, wo hum mein sey nahin."
3936,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab zaani zina kar raha hota hai to wo momin nahin hota. jab shraabi sharab pi raha hota hai to wo momin nahin hota. jab chor chori kar raha hota hai to wo momin nahin hota. jab daaku daaka dal raha hota hai, log uski taraf nazrein utha kar dekhtey hain (ke kitna zalim hai, usey Allah ka khof bilkul nahin) to wo momin nahin hota."
3937,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs loot-maar karta hai, wo hum mein sey nahin."
3938,"Hazrat Solba bin Hakam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : dushman ki kuchh bakriyan hamarey haath lagin, wo hamney loot lein aur haandiyaan chadha din. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) haandiyon key paas sey guzrey to unhen ulat deney ka hukm diya, chunanche wo ulta di gaeen. phir aap ney farmaya : loot halal nahin."
3939,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalman ko gaali dena, fisq (naafarmaani) aur us sey ladna kufr hai."
3940,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalman ko gaali dena, fisq aur us sey ladna kufr hai."
3941,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalman ko gaali dena fisq (nafarmani) aur us sey ladaai karna kufr hai."
3942,"Hazrat Jareer bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Hajjatul-wadaa key moqey par Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : logon ko khamosh karao. (jab log khamosh ho gaey) to aap ney farmaya : merey baad dobara kafir na bin jana ke eik doosrey key galey kaatney lag jao."
3943,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhara bhala ho ! merey baad dobara kafir na bin jana ke eik doosrey key galey kaatney lago."
3944,"Hazrat Sunaabe bin Aa'sir Ahmasi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : suno ! bila shubha main hoz par tumhara pesh-ro hunga. aur bila shubha main dusri ummaton key muqabley mein tumhari kasrat par fakhr karunga, lihaza merey (faut honey key) baad aapas mein ladaai na karna."
3945,"Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney subah ki namaz padhi, wo Allah ki Hifazat mein hai, chunanche tum Allah key (hifz o aman key) wadey ko mat todo. jo shakhs is (namazi musalman) ko qatl kerega, Allah Taala usey (eik mujrim ki tarah apney darbar mein) talab farmaeyga, phir usey jahannam mein munh key bal ondha kar key phenk dega."
3946,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney subah ki namaz padhi, wo Allah ki hifazat mein hai."
3947,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah key yahan momin ki izzat baaz farishton sey bhi ziyada hai."
3948,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs gumrahi key jhandey taley jang karta hai, (logon ko) asbiyat ki dawat deta hai ya asbiyat ki buniyad par ghussey mein aataa hai to uska qatl ho jana jahiliyat ki tarah hai."
3949,"Hazrat Faseela (Raziallahu anha) apney walid (Waasila Isqaa' (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat karti hain, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya ye bhi asbiyat (dushmani) hai ke aadmi apni qom sey mohabbat rakhey? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nahin, asbiyat to ye hai ke aadmi zulm main apni qom ki madad karey."
3950,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri ummat gumrahi par jama nahin hogi, lihaza jab tumhein ikhtilaf nazar aaye to badi jamaat ka sath do."
3951,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney namaz padhi aur usey bahut taweel (lamba) farmaya. jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farigh huye to Sahaba ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! aaj aap ney bahut lambi namaz ada ki hai. aap ney farmaya : mainey talab aur khof wali namaz ada ki hai. mainey Allah sey apni ummat key liye teen chizon ki darkhaast ki thi . Allah Taala ney mujhey do cheezen ata farma den aur eik sawal qubul nahin farmaya. mainey ye darkhaast ki thi ke un par unkey siwa doosrey (ghair muslim) dushman musallat na hon. Allah ney mujhey ye chiz ata farma di. aur mainey Allah sey ye darkhaast ki ke unhen gharq kar key halak na kerey. Allah ney mujhey ye chiz bhi ata farma di. aur mainey us sey ye sawal kiya ke un ki jang aapas main eik doosrey sey na ho. Allah Taala ney meri ye darkhaast qubul nahin farmaai ."
3952,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key azad karda Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey liye zamin sameti gaee yahan tak key mainey uskey mashriq aur maghrib dekh liye, aur mujhey do khazaney diye gaey : zard ya surkh (sona) bhi aur safed (chaandi) bhi, aur mujhey kaha gaya : aap ki saltanat wahan tak hogi jahan tak aap key liye zamin sameti gaee hai. aur mainey Allah sey teen darkhuwasten kin. (eik) ye ke meri ummat par bhook (aur qehat) musallat na karey jis sey un ki aksariyat halak ho jaey. (doosri) ye ke meri ummat par berooni (baahri) dushman musallat ho kar unhen malya-met na kar dey. aur (teesri) ye ke in ko giroh giroh kar key bahami (aapsi) jang mein mubtala na kerey. mujhey farmaya gaya : main jab koi faisla kar leta hun to usey radd nahin kiya ja sakta . main teri ummat par bhook musallat nahin karunga jo unhen halak kar dey, aur main unkey khilaf duniya key kinaron key darmiyan (rehney waley) sab (dushmanon) ko jama nahin karunga balke wo eik doosrey ko tabah kerengey, aur eik doosrey ko qatl kerengey. aur jab meri ummat mein talwaar chal padi to phir qiyamat tak uthai nahin jaaeygi (hamesha chalti rahegi). mujhey apni ummat key barey mein (sab sey ziyada) gumrah karney waley luteron ka khof hai. meri ummat key kuchh qabiley ausan (buton) ki puja kerengey. aur meri ummat key kuchh qabaayel mushrikon sey mil jaeyngey. qiyamat sey pehley tees key qarib jhootey Dajjaal hongey. un mein sey har eik ye daawey kerega ke wo Nabi hai. meri ummat mein sey eik jamaat hamesha haq par qaaim rahegi. un ki madad ki jaeygi. unkey mukhalif unhen nuqsan nahin pahuncha sakengey yahan tak key Allah ka hukm aa jaeyga. Imam Ibne-Maja key shagrid Abul-Hasan Qataan (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : jab Imam Abu-Adbullah (Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah)) ye hadees suna kar farigh huye to farmaya : kis qadr khof-zada karney wali hadees hai !"
3953,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Zenab binte Jahash (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (eik din) neend sey bedaar huye to aap ka chehra Mubarak surkh tha aur aap farma rahey they : eik Allah key siwa koi haqeeqi mabood nahin. Arbon ki tabahi hai us shar ki wajeh sey jo qarib hai. aaj Yajuj Majuj ki deewar mein itna rakhna paida ho gaya hai. aur (ye farmatey huye) aap ney haathon sey das ka ishara farmaya. Ummul-mominin Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya hum tabah ho jaeyngey jabke hamarey andar nek log bhi mojud hongey? aap ney farmaya : (haan) jab buraai ziyada ho jaeygi."
3954,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (mustaqbil mein) aisey fitney barpa hongey jin mein aadmi subah ko momin hoga to Sham ko kafir ho jaeyga (aur Sham ko momin hoga to subah ko kafir ho jaeyga). magar jisey Allah ilm key zariey sey zinda rakhey."
3955,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : hum log Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key paas bethey they ke unhoney farmaya : tum mein sey kisi ko fitney key barey mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki koi hadees yad hai? Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : mainey kaha : mujhey yad hai. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : tum jur'at mand ho. phir farmaya (wo hadees) kis tarah hai? Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : aadmi ko uskey ehal aur ayaal aur padausiyon key barey mein jo aazmaaish aati hai, uski maafi namaz, rozey , sadqey , bhalaai ka hukm dene se aur buraai ke rokne sey ho jati hai. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mera ye maqsad nahin. (is sawal sey) mera maqsad wo fitna hai jo samandar ki tarah tez tufaani hoga. unhoney kaha : Ameerul-momineen ! aap ko is sey kya khatra hai? aap key aur us (fitney) key darmiyan to eik band darwaza hai. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : wo darwaza toot jaeyga ya khul jaeyga? Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : nahin, balke toot jaeyga. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : iska taqaza to ye hai ke wo (dobara) band nahin hoga. Hazrat Shaqeeq (Rahimahullah) ney bayan kiya : hum logon ney Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : kya Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko malum tha ke wo darwaza kon hai? Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : haan, (unhen is qadr yaqeeni malum tha) jaisey ye malum hota hai ke kal ka din aaney sey pehley raat aayegi. mainey unhen eik hadees sunai thi jo ghalat-salat (ghalat aur manghadat) nahin thi. (Hazrat Shaqeeq (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : ) hamen un sey ye poochhtey huye khof mehsus huwa ke wo darwaza kon tha? (kahin musalsal sawalat sey narazi mehsus na karen) chunanche hamney Masruq (Rahimahullah) sey kaha : un sey ye baat poochhnaa. Masruq ney un sey puchha (ke fitnon mein rukawat shakhsiyat kon hai )?  to Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu)."
3956,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abd Rabbe Kaba (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa jabke aap Kabey key saye mein bethey they aur log aap key paas jama they. mainey aap ko ye farmatey huye suna : hum Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath eik safar mein they. aap eik manzil par utrey , hum mein sey koi khema laga raha tha, koi (tafrih key tor par) teer andazi kar raha tha aur koi apney maweshiyon ki dekh bhaal mein masroof tha. achcha (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key) aelan karney waley ney aelan kiya : sab log namaz key liye jama ho jaeyn. hum sab jama ho gaey. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (namaz key baad) uth kar khutba irshad farmaya. aap ney farmaya : mujh sey pehley jo bhi Nabi aaya , uska farz tha ke usey jo bhalai malum hai apni qom ko bataey aur usey jo burai malum hai us sey unhein daraaiye. is ummat ki aafiyat uskey pehley hissey mein hai aur aakhir walon ko aisi aazmaaishein ayengi aur aisey maamlat pesh ayengey jin ko tum ajeeb mehsus karogey, phir fitney pesh ayengey jo eik doosrey ko maamuli bana dengey. (baad wala fitna dekh kar malum hoga ke is sey to pehla hi halka tha). momin kaheyga : ye fitna mujhey tabah kar dega. phir wo (fitna) khatam ho jaeyga. phir (doosra) fitna aayega to momin kaheyga : ye mujhey tabah kar dega . phir wo khatam ho jaeyga, lihaza jisey ye baat pasand hai ke wo jahannam sey bach jaey aur jannat mein dakhil kar diya jaey, usey chahiye ke usey maut aaye to wo Allah par aur aakhirat key din par eman rakhta ho aur logon sey aisa sulook karey jaisa wo chahta hai ke log us sey karen. aur jisney kisi (sharae) Imam ki baiat ki, us sey haath mila kar ehad kiya aur us ko apney dil ka khulus pesh kiya to usey chahiye ke jahan tak mumkin ho uski itaat karey. agar koi doosra shakhs aa kar us (khalifa) sey khincha taani karey (us sey hukumat chheenney ki koshish kerey) to us doosrey (muddai khilaafat) ki gardan uda do. Abdur-Rehman (Rahimahullah) bayan farmatey hain : mainey logon key darmiyan apna sar aagey nikala aur kaha : main aap ko Allah ki qism dey kar poochhta hun kya aap ney ye farman khud Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna hai? Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney apney haath sey apney kanon ki taraf ishara kartey huye farmaya : isey merey dono kanon ney suna aur merey dil ney yad rakha hai."
3957,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is zamaney main tumhara kya haal hoga jo anqarib aaney wala hai, jis mein logon ko khub chhan liya jaeyga. (ehale eman aur achchhey aadmi utha liye jaeyngey) aur chhaan-buraa baqi reh jaeyga (be-deen aur razeel log baqi reh jaeyngey) jinkey ehad aur mawaaeed mein be-wafai aur amanaton mein khayanat hogi aur un mein is tarah sey ikhtilaf ho jaeyga. ye farmatey waqt Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apney haathon ki ungliyon ko eik dusri key andar dal kar dikhaya. Sahaba ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! jab ye soorate-haal ho to hum kya keren? aap ney farmaya : jo baat tumhen (Quran aur sunnat ki roshni mein) sahih malum ho usey ikhtiyar karo aur jo baat (Quran aur sunnat ki roshni mein) ghalat malum ho usey chhod do. aur apney khas afrad (ehle-khana, aqaarib, mukhlis dost waghera) par tawajjoh do aur aam logon key maamlat sey eik taraf ho jao."
3958,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Abu-Zar ! us waqt to kya kerega jab logon mein maut kasrat sey waqey hogi yahan tak key eik ghar , yani qabr ki qeemat eik ghulam key barabar hogi? mainey kaha : (main wohi kuch karunga) jo kuchh merey liye Allah aur uska Rasool pasand farmaeyn. ya mainey kaha : Allah aur uska Rasool behtar jantey hain (ke mujhey un halaat mein kya karna chahiye). aap ney farmaya : sabr karna. phir aap ney farmaya : to kya kerega jab logon ko bhook ka samna hoga yahan tak key to masjid mein aayega to tujh sey apney bistar tak wapis nahin pahuncha jaeyga aur to apney bistar sey uth kar apni namaz ki jagah tak nahin ja sakeyga? mainey kaha : Allah aur uska Rasool behtar jantey hain. ya kaha : jo kuchh Allah aur uska Rasool merey liye pasand farmaeyn. aap ney farmaya : iffat ikhtiyar karna. phir farmaya : to kya kerega jab logon mein qatl aur gharat aam hogi yahan tak key Hijaartuzz Zait (ka maqam) khoon mein doob jaeyga? mainey kaha : jo kuchh Allah aur uska Rasool merey liye pasand farmaain . aap ney farmaya : to jis qabiley sey hai usi mein ja rehna. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kyon na main talwaar ley kar un logon ko qatl karun jo ye (fasad) kerengey? aap ney farmaya : tab to to logon key sath (jang aur jadl mein) shareek ho gaya, balke us soorate haal main to apney ghar mein dakhil ho jana. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! agar log merey ghar mein ghus ayen to? aap ney farmaya : agar tujhey khatra ho ke talwaar ki chamak tujh par ghalib aa jaeygi to apni chadar ka kinara apney chehrey par dal lena. tab wo (fasaadi qatil) apna aur tera gunah utha ley jaeyga aur wo jahannami ho jaeyga."
3959,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat sey pehley haraj waqey hoga . mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! haraj ka kya matlab hai? aap ney farmaya : qatl aur gharat. kuchh musalmanon ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! ab bhi to hum saal bhar mein itney itney mushrikon ko qatl kar detey hain. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mushrikon ka qatl nahin hoga balke tum log eik doosrey ko qatl karogey yahan tak key aadmi apney padosi ko , apney chacha zaad ko aur apney rishte-daar ko qatl kar dega. baaz afrad ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya us daur mein hamari aqlen hamarey sath hongi ? aap ney farmaya : nahin, us zamaney mein aksar logon ki aqlen chhin jaeyngi. aur baad mein aisey log aa jaeyngey jo gardo-ghubar ki tarah (be-haqeeqat, be-qadr) hongey. unkey paas aqlen nahin hongi. phir Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : qism hai Allah ki ! mujhey to lagta hai ke wo fitna mujh par aur tum logon hi par aa jaeyga. aur qism hai Allah ki ! agar ye us chiz key barey mein huwa jis key barey mein hamein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney nasihat farmaai thi to merey aur tumharey liye us sey nikalney ka koi raasta nahin hoga, siwaye iskey ke jis tarah hum is mein shamil huye they, isi tarah nikal jaeyn."
3960,"Hazrat Udaisa binte Ahbaan (Reh.) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : jab Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) yahan Basra mein tashrif laye to merey walid (Hazrat Ahbaan bin Saifi Ghifaari (Raziallahu anhu)) key paas bhi aaye, unhoney farmaya : Abu-Muslim ! (Ahbaan (Raziallahu anhu)) kya aap un logon (Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) aur unkey sathiyon) key khilaf meri madad nahin kerengey? Ahbaan (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : kyon nahin, phir apni eik londi ko bula kar kaha : londi ! meri talwaar nikal. wo talwaar ley aai. unhoney miyaan sey eik baalisht talwaar bahar nikali to (maloom huwa ke) wo lakdi ki thi. unhoney farmaya : merey mehbub aur terey chacha key betey (Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) ney mujhey ye nasihat ki thi ke jab musalmanon mein baham (aapas mein) fitna aur fasad barpa ho jaey to main lakdi ki talwaar bana lun. ab agar aap chahtey hain to main aap key sath (lakdi ki talwaar ley kar) chalney ko tayyar hun. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mujhey na to aap ki zaroorat hai aur na aap ki talwaar ki."
3961,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat sey pehley aisey fitney (roonumaa) hongey jaisey taareek (andheri) raat key tukdey. un mein insan subah ko momin hoga to Sham ko kafir ho jaeyga aur Sham ko momin hoga to subah ko kafir ho jaeyga. un (fitnon) key doran mein betha huwa khadey huye sey , khada huwa chalney waley sey aur chalney wala bhagney waley sey behtar hoga . un halaat main tum apni kamaanein tod dena, un ki taant kaat dena aur apni talwaarein patharon par dey maarna. agar (fasaadi log) tum mein sey kisi key ghar mein ghus ayen to Aadam (Alaihissalam) key do beton mein sey achchhey betey (Haabeel) ki tarah ho jana."
3962,"Hazrat Abu-Barda (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main Hazrat Muhammad bin Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa to unhoney bayan kiya : be-shak Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : anqarib fitna, farq aur ikhtilaf (saamne) hoga. jab ye soorate-haal pesh aaye to apni talwaar ley kar uhad pahad par chadh jana aur usey (pahad key patharon par) maar kar tod dena. phir ghar mein bethe rehna yahan tak key tujh tak koi gunah-gaar haath pahunch jaey ya faisla kar deney wali maut aa jaey. (Muhammad bin Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : ) tehqiqi fitna waqey ho chuka aur mainey wohi kuchh kiya jo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha."
3963,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab do musalman apni talwaarein ley kar eik doosrey key muqabil hotey hain to qatil aur maqtool (dono) jahannam mein jatey hain."
3964,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab do musalman apni talwaarein ley kar eik doosrey sey (ladney key liye) miltey hain to qatil aur maqtool (dono fareeq) jahannam mein jaeyngey. Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! ye qatil hai (isliye mujrim hai) maqtool (key jahannami honey) ki kya wajeh hai? aap ney farmaya : wo bhi apney sathi ko qatl karna chahta tha."
3965,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab do musalmanon mein sey eik apney bhai par hathiyar uthata hai to wo dono jahannam key kinarey par hotey hain. jab un mein sey eik apney sathi ko qatl kar deta hai to dono jahannam mein dakhil ho jatey hain."
3966,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din Allah key yahan sab sey burey darjey wala shakhs wo hoga jisney (doosrey ki) duniya key liye apni aakhirat zaya kar li."
3967,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : anqarib eik aisa fitna barpa hoga jo Arbon ka safaayaa kar dega . uskey maqtool jahannam mein jaeyngey. us fitney mein zaban talwaar key waar sey ziyada sakht (aur takleef deh) mehsus hogi."
3968,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : fitnon sey bacho , un mein zaban (ki baat) talwaar key waar ki tarah (asar andaz) hoti hai."
3969,"Hazrat Alqama bin Waqas (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unkey paas sey eik aadmi guzra jo (muaashrey mein) ooncha maqam rakhta tha. Alqama (Rahimahullah) ney us sey kaha : tera (mujh sey) qurbat ka talluq hai aur (mujh par) tera haq hai. (isliye nasihat key tor par baat kar raha hun). mainey dekha hai ke to un hukmranon key paas jata hai, aur un sey , jo Allah chahey , baat cheet karta hai. mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Sahaba Hazrat Bilal bin Haris Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) sey suna hai, unhoney kaha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi shakhs Allah ko razi karney wali eik baat karta hai, wo nahin samajhta ke uska wahan tak asar hoga jahan tak (haqeeqat mein) ho jata hai. uski wajeh sey Allah uskey liye qiyamat tak apni khushnoodi likh deta hai. aur eik aadmi Allah ki narazi wali eik baat karta hai, wo nahin samajhta ke uska wahan tak asar hoga jahan tak (haqeeqat mein) ho jata hai. uski wajeh sey Allah uskey liye us din tak apni narazi likh deta hai jis din us sey mulaqat hogi. Alqama (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : isliye dekh liya kar ke to kya keh raha hai aur kya kuchh munh sey nikal raha hai, tera bhala ho. mujhey to Bilal bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) sey suni hui ye hadees kaee baaten kehney sey rok deti hai."
3970,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi (baaz oqaat) Allah ki narazi wala eik lafz keh deta hai, wo is mein harj nahin samajhta. (lekin wo itna bade gunah ka lafz hota hai ke) wo uski wajeh sey sattar saal tak jahannam mein gir jata hai."
3971,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah par aur qiyamat key din par eman rakhta hai, usey chahiye ke achchhi baat kahey ya khamosh rahey."
3972,"Hazrat Sufiyan bin Abdullah Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! mujhey (nasihat ki) eik baat farma dijiye jis par main mazbooti sey qaaim rahun. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kaho : mera Rab Allah hai, phir is par mazbooti sey qaaim raho. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ko merey barey mein sab sey ziyada kis chiz sey (nuqsan pahunchney ka) khof hai? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apni zabane Mubarak ko pakda, phir farmaya : is sey."
3973,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main eik safar mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath tha, eik din jabkey hum chal rahey they main aap key qarib ho gaya . mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! mujhey aisa amal bataiye jo mujhey jannat mein pahuncha dey aur jahannam sey door kar dey . aap ney farmaya : tu ney badi azeem baat poochhi hai aur jis key liye Allah aasan kar dey uskey liye ye aasan bhi hai. (jannat mein pahunchane-wala amal ye hai ke) to Allah ki ibadat karey , uskey sath kisi ko shareek na karey , namaz qaaim karey , zakat ada karey , Ramzan key rozey rakhey aur Baitullah ka Haj kerey. phir farmaya : kya main tujhey neki key darwazey na bataun? roza dhaal hai. sadqa gunah (ki aag) ko bujha deta hai, jaisey pani aag ko bujha deti hai. aur aadmi ka raat key doran mein namaz (tahajjud) padhna. phir aap ney ye aayat tilawat farmaai : (تَتَجَافَىٰ جُنُوبُهُمْ عَنِ ٱلْمَضَاجِعِ . . . جَزَآءًۢ بِمَا كَانُوا يَعْمَلُونَ),''un key pehlu bistaron sey alag rehtey hain. (aur) wo apney Rab ko khof aur ummid sey pukartey hain, aur jo kuchh hamney unhen rizq diya hai, is mein sey kharch kartey hain. koi nafs nahin janta ke unkey aamaal key badley mein unkey liye aakhon ki thandak ki kon kon si cheezen poshida rakhi gaee hain.'' phir farmaya : kya main tujhey Deen ka sar, uska sutoon aur uski kohaan ki choti na bataun? wo jihad hai. phir farmaya : main tujhey wo chiz na bataun jis par un sab ka madaar hai? mainey kaha : kyon nahin ! tab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apni zaban pakad kar farmaya : isey rok kar rakhna. mainey kaha : Allah key Nabi ! hum jo baaten kartey hain kya un par bhi hamari poochh-gachchh hogi? aap ney farmaya : Muaz ! teri maa tujhey roey. logon ko (jahannam ki) aag mein chehron key bal ghaseetney wali chiz un ki zabanon ki kaati hui faslon key siwa aur kya hai?"
3974,"Ummul-mominin Umme-Habiba (bint Abu-Sufiyaan) (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Adam key betey ka har kalam uskey khilaf hai, uskey haq mein nahin, siwaye neki ka hukm deney, burai sey mana karney aur Allah ka zikr karney key."
3975,"Hazrat Abu-Sha'shaa (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, kisi ney Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey kaha : hum Ameeron (hukmranon) key paas jatey hain to eik baat kehtey hain, phir jab hum bahar aatey hain to dusri baat kehtey hain. Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : is chiz ko hum Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein munafiqat shumar kartey they."
3976,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye bhi insan key Islam ki khoobi hai ke jis mamley sey uska talluq nahin usey chhod dey."
3977,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : logon key liye behtareen zindagi ye hai ke aadmi Allah ki raah mein apney ghodey ki baag pakdey, uski peeth par beth kar (maidaane jang mein) udtaa phirta ho, jab bhi khof-zada karney wali ya pareshan-kun aawaz sunai dey, wo is par udhar ud jata hai. wo maut ya shahadat ko uski jagahon mein talash karta phirta hai. ya eik aadmi kisi choti par ya kisi wadi mein chand bakriyan ley kar reh raha hai, wo namaz qaaim karta hai, zakat ada karta hai aur martey dam tak apney Rab ki ibadat karta rehta hai. logon key sath sirf neki key maamlat mein talluq rakhta hai."
3978,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, eik aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar sawal kiya : kon sa insan afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : Allah ki raah main apni jaan aur maal key sath jihad karney wala. usney kaha : uskey baad kon sa (afzal hai)? aap ney farmaya : wo aadmi jo kisi ghaati mein Allah ki ibadat karta hai, logon ko apney shar sey bachaey rakhta hai."
3979,"Hazrat Huzefa bin Yamaan (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kuchh log hongey jo jahannam key darwazon par khadey ho kar logon ko (jahannam ki taraf) bulaeyngey. jo shakhs un ki baat maaneyga wo usey jahannam mein phenk dengey. mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! hamein unkey osaaf (aur alaamaat) bata dijiye. aap ney farmaya : wo hum hi mein sey kuchh afrad hongey aur hamari zabanon hi mein baat kerengey. mainey kaha : agar mujhey (un ka) ye zamana miley to aap mujhey kya hukm detey hain? aap ney farmaya : musalmanon ki ijtamaaiyat aur unkey Imam key sath pewasta rehna. agar un ki ijtamaaiyat na ho aur na koi (muttafiqa) Imam ho to un sab firqon sey alag rehna agar-che tujhey kisi darkht ki jad chaabni padey yahan tak key tujhey usi haal mein maut aa jaey."
3980,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qarib hai ke musalman key liye behtareen maal bakriyan hon jin ko pahadon ki chotiyon aur barish ki jagahon mein (jahan ghaas chaara mil sakta hai) liye phirta rahey. aur (is tarah) apney Deen ko fitnon sey bachaney key liye (fitnon sey door) bhaagtaa phirey."
3981,"Hazrat Huzefa bin Yamaan (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : fitney paida hongey unkey darwazon par jahannam ki taraf bulaney waley hongey . un mein sey kisi key peechhey lagney sey behtar hai ke to kisi darkht ki jad chabaataa huwa mar jaey."
3982,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : momin eik surakh sey do baar nahin dasaa jata."
3983,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : momin eik surakh sey do baar nahin dasaa jata."
3984,"Imam Shaabey (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhuma) ko member par apney kanon ki taraf ungliyon sey ishara kar key ye farmatey suna : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : halal wazeh hai aur haram (bhi) wazeh hai aur un dono key darmiyan kuchh shubha wali cheezen hain, jin sey aksar log waqif nahin. to jisney shubha wali chizon sey ijtinab (parhez) kiya usney apney Deen aur apni izzat ko bacha liya aur jo koi shubha wali chizon mein mubtala ho gaya, wo haram mein mubtala ho jaeyga, jaisey mamnoo charaagaah key ird-gird bakriyan charaney wala, ho sakta hai ke (naa-daanista tor par) uskey andar (janwer) charaa ley (aur is tarah mujrim qarar paa jaey). khabrdar ! har badshah ki eik mamnoo (mana ki hui) charaagaah hoti hai (jis mein aam logon key janweron ka dakhila mamnoo (manaa) hota hai). khabrdar ! Allah ki mamnoo charaagaah sey murad Allah ki haram karda cheezen (aur kaam) hain. sun lo ! jism mein gosht ka eik tukda hai, agar wo sahih ho to sara jism sahih hota hai, agar wo kharab ho jaey to sara jism kharab ho jata hai. suno ! wo dil hai."
3985,"Hazrat Maaqil bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qatl aur gharat (aur fitnon key dinon) key doran mein ibadat karna aisey hai jaisey meri taraf hijrat karna."
3986,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Islam shuru mein ajnabi tha, aur wo dobara ajnabi ho jaeyga, isliye ajnabiyon ko Mubarak ho."
3987,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Islam shuru mein ajnabi tha, aur wo dobara ajnabi ho jaeyga, isliye ajnabiyon ko Mubarak ho."
3988,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Islam ajnabi key tor par shuru huwa , aur wo dobara ajnabi ho jaeyga. to ajnabiyon ko Mubarak ho. arz kiya gaya : ajnabi (ghurba) kon hain? aap ney farmaya : qabaayel sey alag honey waley."
3989,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, wo eik din Masjide-Nabuwi mein tashrif ley gaey to dekha ke Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qabr Mubarak key paas bethey ro rahey hain. unhoney kaha : aap kyon ro rahey hain? Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suney huye eik irshad ki wajeh sey ronaa aa raha hai. mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : thoda sa dikhawa bhi shirk hai. aur jo koi Allah key kisi dost sey dushmani rakhta hai, wo (goya) Allah Taala key khilaf aelane-jang karta hai. Allah Taala ko wo gumnaam muttaqi nek log pasand hain jo ghair hazir hon to unhen talash nahin kiya jata, agar mojud hon to unhen bulaya nahin jata, na unhen pehchaanaa jata hai. unkey dil hidayat key chiragh hain. wo har eik ghubar aalud taareek fitney sey nikal jatey hain (aur fitnon sey mutassir ho kar gumrah nahin hotey)."
3990,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : logon ki misal un sau oonton ki si hai jin mein sey eik bhi sawari key qabil na miley."
3991,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : yahudi  (71) firqon mein taqseem huye . aur meri ummat (73) firqon mein taqseem ho jaeygi."
3992,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Yahudi 71 firqon mein taqseem huye. (un mein sey) eik firqa jannati tha aur sattar jahannami. Esai behttar (72) firqon mein taqseem huye. (un mein sey) ikhattar jahannami they aur eik jannati. qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki jaan hai ! meri ummat zarur tehattar firqon mein bat jaaeygi. (un mein sey) eik firqa jannat mein jaeyga aur behttar jahannam mein. arz kiya gaya : Allah key Rasool ! wo kon log hain? farmaya : jamaat."
3993,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Bani-Israel ikhattar  firqon mein taqseem huye aur meri ummat behtar bahattar firqon mein taqseem ho jaeygi. eik key siwa wo sab firqey jahannam mein jaeyngey, aur wo jamaat hai."
3994,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum log pahlon key tareeqey ki (puri tarah) perwi karogey, jaisey do haatho ke faasle key barabar, haath haath key barabar , aur baalisht baalisht key barabar hoti hai yahan tak key agar wo kisi saandey key bil mein ghusey hongey to tum bhi zarur is mein ghusogey. Sahaba ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kya yahudiyon aur esaiyon ki (perwi kerengey)? aap ney farmaya : aur kin ki?"
3995,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khadey ho kar logon ko khutba diya, aur farmaya : logo, qism hai Allah ki ! mujhey tumharey barey mein sirf duniya ki zeenat (aur maal aur dolat) sey khatra hai jo Allah Taala tumhen ata farmaeyga. eik aadmi ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! kya khair sey bhi shar hasil ho jata hai? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) thodi der khamosh rahey, phir farmaya : tum ney kya sawal kiya? usney kaha : mainey kaha tha : kya khair sey bhi shar hasil hota hai? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khair (halal maal) sey khair hi hasil hota hai, kya wo khair hai? (duniya ka har maal khair nahin hota). mausame-bahar mein jo sabza ugta hai us sey janwer aphaarey ka shikar ho kar mar jata hai ya marney key qarib ho jata hai, magar wo charney wala janwer (bach jata hai) jo khata hai, phir jab uski kokhein bhar jati hain to dhoop ki taraf munh kar key gobar aur peshab karta hai, phir jugaali karta hai. uskey baad dobara khaney lagta hai. jo shakhs jayez tareeqey sey maal hasil karta hai usey is mein barkat hasil hoti hai. aur jo shakhs najaayiz tareeqey sey maal hasil karta hai uski misal aisey hai jaisey koi khata rehta hai lekin sair nahin hota."
3996,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum Faras aur Rome (ki saltanaton) key khazaney Fateh kar logey to tumhari kya haalat hogi? Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : hum wohi kuchh (shukar key kalimaat) kahengey (aur shukar waley amal kerengey) jinka Allah ney hamein hukm diya hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ya dusri baat hogi. tum eik doosrey par rashk karogey, phir eik doosrey sey hasad karogey, phir eik doosrey sey munh pherogey, phir eik doosrey sey naraz rehney lagogey. ya is tarah ka koi aur lafz farmaya. phir tum gharib muhajrin mein jaogey aur unhen eik doosrey ki gardanon par laad dogey."
3997,"Hazrat Amr bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, wo bano Aamir bin Looie key haleef (dost) they aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath ghazwae-badar mein shareek huye they. unhoney bayan kiya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah (Raziallahu anhu) ko Behrein rawana farmaya taake wahan (key logon) ka jiziya ley kar aaeyn. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Behrein walon sey suleh ki thi aur un par Hazrat Alaa bin Hizrami (Raziallahu anhu) ko ameer muqarrar farmaya tha. Hazrat Abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) Behrein sey maal ley kar aaye. Ansaar ko Hazrat abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) ki aamad ka ilm huwa to unhoney Fajr ki namaz (Masjide-Nabawi mein) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein ada ki. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab namaz sey farigh huye to wo log aap key samney aaye. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen dekha to muskura diye, phir farmaya : mera khayal hai, tum ney suna hai ke Abu-Ubaida Behrein sey kuch laye hain? unhoney kaha : ji haan, Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : khush ho jao aur khushi wali chizon ki ummid rakho. qism hai Allah ki ! mujhey tum par faqr (ghareebi) ka andesha nahin. mujhey to ye khatra hai ke duniya tum par isi tarah faraakh ho jaeygi jis tarah tum sey pehley logon par hui thi, phir tum uskey liye eik doosrey par rashk (aur eik doosre se badh jaane ki koshish) karogey jis tarah tum sey pehley logon ney kiya, to ye (duniya) tumhen tabah kar degi jis tarah usney tum sey pehley logon ko tabah kar diya tha."
3998,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main apney baad mardon key liye aurton sey bada koi fitna nahin chhodta."
3999,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har subah do farishtey aelan kartey hain : mardon key liye aurton ki wajeh sey halakat hai. aur aurton key liye mardon ki wajeh sey halakat hai."
4000,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khadey ho kar khutba diya. is mein aap ney ye bhi farmaya : ye duniya sar sabz (hara) aur meethi hai. Allah Taala tumhen is mein (doosron ka) khalifa bana kar ye dekhega ke tum log kaisey amal kartey ho. khabrdar ! duniya (key shar) sey bacho aur aurton (ki wajeh sey gumrah honey) sey bacho."
4001,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein bethey they ke qabila Muzena ki eik aurat zeenat wala libas pehney itrati hui masjid mein aai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : logo ! apni aurton ko masjid mein zeenat wala libas pehanney aur tafaakhur (ghamand) wali chaal chalney sey mana karo. Bani-Israel par usi waqt lanat ki gaee thi jab un ki aurton ney zeenat wala libas pehna aur masjidon mein fakhr sey chalney lagin."
4002,"Hazrat abu-Raham (Raziallahu anhu) key azad karda Hazrat Ubaid (bin Kasir (Rahimahullah)) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko eik aurat mili jisney khushbu laga rakhi thi aur masjid ki taraf ja rahi thi. Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Jabbaar ki bandi ! kahan ja rahi ho? usney kaha : masjid mein. farmaya : isi liye khushbu lagai hai? usney kaha : ji haan. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : jo aurat khushbu laga kar masjid ki taraf chaley uski namaz qubul nahin hoti jab tak ghusl na kar ley."
4003,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey aurton ki jamaat ! sadqa kiya karo aur kasrat sey istighfar kiya karo. mainey jahannam mein tumhari tadaad sab sey ziyada dekhi hai. eik aql-mand khatoon ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! iski kya wajeh hai ke jahannam mein hamari tadaad ziyada hai? aap ney farmaya : tum (gaali galoch aur) fitkaar, taana ziyada karti ho aur rafeeqe-hayaat ki nashukri karti ho. mainey nahin dekha ke aql aur Deen mein naqis honey key bawajud koi chiz aql-mand aadmi par tum sey ziyada ghalib aati ho. usney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! aql aur Deen ka naqs kon sa hai? farmaya : aql ki kami to ye hai ke do aurton ki gawahi eik mard ki gawahi key barabar hoti hai. ye uski aql ki kami ki wajeh sey hai. aur wo (mahiney mein) kaee din namaz nahin padhti aur Ramzan mein (un dinon mein) roza nahin rakh sakti, ye Deen ka naqs hai."
4004,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : neki ka hukm do aur burai sey mana karo, qabl iskey ke tum duayen maango aur tumhari duayen qubul na ki jaaeyn."
4005,"Hazrat Qais bin Abu-Haazim (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ney khadey ho kar Allah ki hamd aur sanaa bayan ki, phir farmaya : aey logo ! tum ye aayat padhtey ho : (یٰاَیُّهَا الَّذِیْنَ اٰمَنُوْا عَلَیْكُمْ اَنْفُسَكُمْ لَا یَضُرُّكُمْ مَّنْ ضَلَّ اِذَا اهْتَدَیْتُمْ), ''aey eman walo ! tum apney aap ko sidha rakho. jab tum hidayat par ho to gumrah log tumhen nuqsan nahin pahuncha sakengey."" aur hamney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : log jab burai ko dekhen aur usey khatam na karen (us sey mana na keren) to qarib hai ke Allah Taala un sab ko azab ki lapet mein ley ley. hadees key Raavi Abu-Usaama ney dusri martaba riwayat bayan kartey huye kaha : (Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha) mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they."
4006,"Hazrat Abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Bani-Israel mein naqaayis is tarah paida huye ke aadmi apney bhai ko (eik baar) koi gunah kartey dekhta to usey mana karta, phir agley din usey gunah kartey dekhta to uski wajeh sey wo uska hum niwaala, ham piyala aur hum raz banney sey na ruktaa, chunanche Allah Taala ney unkey dil eik doosrey sey mila diye. unkey barey mein Quran nazil huwa. Allah Taala ney farmaya : (لُعِنَ الَّذِیْنَ كَفَرُوْا مِنْۢ بَنِیْۤ اِسْرَآءِیْلَ . . كَثِیْرًا مِّنْهُمْ فٰسِقُوْنَ), ''bani Israel key kafiron par Hazrat Dawud aur Hazrat Esa ibne Maryam ki zabani lanat ki gaee, is wajeh sey ke wo nafarmaniyan kartey they aur had sey badh jatey they aur wo jo burey kaam kartey they, un sey eik doosrey ko mana nahin kartey they. wo jo kuchh kartey they yaqinan bahut bura tha. un mein sey bahut sey logon ko aap dekhengey ke kafiron sey dosti kartey hain. bahut bura hai jo kuchh unhoney apney liye aagey bheja. wo ye ke Allah Taala un sey naraz huwa, aur wo hamesha azab mein rahengey. aur agar wo Allah par, Nabi par aur Nabi par nazil honey wali shariyat par eman rakhney waley hotey to un (kafiron) sey dosti na kartey lekin un mein sey aksar fasiq hain.'' Hazrat Abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tek lagaey huye they, aap sidhey ho kar beth gaey aur farmaya : nahin (tum azab sey nahin bach saktey) yahan tak key zalim ka haath pakad kar (usey zulm sey rok do aur) usey haq qubul karney par majbur kar do. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney yehi riwayat eik dusri sanad sey Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey isi tarah marfooan bhi bayan ki hai."
4007,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khutba deney key liye khadey huye to aap ney is mein ye bhi farmaya : khabrdar ! kisi aadmi ko logon ki haibat haq kehney sey rok na dey jabke usey (haq) malum ho. ye keh kar Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ro padey aur farmaya : qism hai Allah ki ! hamney kaee (ghalat) cheezen dekhin lekin (izhar karney sey) dar gaey."
4008,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi shakhs apney aap ko zaleel na kerey. Sahaba ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! koi shakhs apney aap ko kis tarah zaleel karta hai? aap ney farmaya : wo aisa kaam hota dekhta hai jis key barey mein Allah ki taraf sey is par bolnaa zaruri hai, phir wo uskey barey mein baat nahin karta, (aur ghalat kaam sey mana nahin karta) usey qiyamat key din Allah Taala farmaeyga : tujhey falan masley mein baat karney sey kya rukawat thi? wo kaheyga : logon ka khof tha. Allah Taala farmaeyga : tera ziyada haq mujh hi sey darney ka tha."
4009,"Hazrat Jareer bin Abdullah Bijli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jin logon mein Allah ki nafarmani ki jaey jabke wo (gunah karney walon sey) ziyada taqatwar aur ziyada zor-aawar hon, iskey bawajud (mujrimon ko gunah sey) mana na karen to Allah Taala un sab par azab nazil kar deta hai."
4010,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab samandar ka safar tey karney waley Muhajir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye to aap ney farmaya : kya tum log mujhey wo ajeeb baaten nahin bataogey jo tum ney Habsha key mulk mein dekhin? un mein sey kuchh nojawan afrad ney kaha : ji haan, Allah key Rasool ! (hum sunaeyn gey). eik baar hum bethey huye they ke hamarey paas sey un ki eik raahib budhiya guzri jisney sar par pani ka matka uthaya huwa tha. wo un mein sey eik jawan (ladkey) key paas sey guzri to usney us (raahiba) key kandhon key darmiyan haath rakh kar usey dhakkaa dey diya. wo ghutnon key bal giri. uska matka toot gaya. jab wo uthi to us (shareer ladkey) ki taraf mud kar boli : aray dhokey baaz ! tujhey tab pata chalega jab Allah Taala (hashr key maidan mein) kursi rakhega aur tamam pahlon aur pichhlon ko jama kerega aur (insanon key) haath aur paon unkey amalon ki gawahi dengey. phir tujhey pata chaleyga ke kal (qiyamat ko) us (Allah) key paas mera tera maamla kaisey tey hota hai? Raavi ney kaha : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (ye waqiyaa sun kar) farmaya : usney sach kaha. usney sach kaha. Allah Taala us qom ko kyonkar paak kerega jin mein taqatwar sey kamzor ko haq nahin dilwaya jata?"
4011,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sab sey afzal jihad zalim sultaan key samney insaf (aur haq) ki baat kehna hai."
4012,Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi pehley jamre key qarib Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key samney aaya aur kaha : Allah key Rasool ! kon sa jihad afzal hai? aap khamosh rahey. jab aap doosrey jamre par pahunchey to usney (phir) sawal kiya. aap khamosh rahey. phir jab aap ney Jamrae-Aqba (badey jamre) par kankariyaan maarin aur sawar honey key liye rikaab mein paon rakha to farmaya : sawal karney wala kahan hai? usney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! main hun. aap ney farmaya : zalim sultaan key samney haq ka kalma kehna (afzal jihad hai).
4013,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Marwan ney Eid key din member nikalwaayaa (aur Eid-gaah mein rakha) aur Namaze-Eid sey pehley khutba shuru kiya. eik aadmi ney kaha : Marwan ! tu ney sunnat ki mukhalifat ki hai. tu ney is din member nikala, halanke (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur khulafae-Rashidin key zamaney mein) wo nahin nikala jata tha. aur tu ney namaz sey pehley khutba shuru kiya, halanke (us daur mein) khutbey sey ibtida (shuruat) nahin ki jati thi. Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya is shakhs ney apna farz ada kar diya hai. mainey Rasoolullah sey suna , aap farma rahey they : tum mein sey jo shakhs koi burai dekhey aur haath sey khatam kar sakta ho to haath sey khatam kar dey. agar uski taqat na ho to zaban sey (mana karey aur samjhaaye). agar uski bhi taqat na ho to dil sey (nafrat karey aur uskey khatime ki khahish rakhey). aur ye sab sey kamzor eman hai."
4014,"Hazrat Abu Umaamiya Shaobaani (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Abu-Solba Khushni (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : aap ka is aayat key barey mein kya khayal hai? farmaya : kon si aayat? mainey kaha : (یٰاَیُّهَا الَّذِیْنَ اٰمَنُوْا عَلَیْكُمْ اَنْفُسَكُمْ لَا یَضُرُّكُمْ مَّنْ ضَلَّ اِذَا اهْتَدَیْتُمْ),''aey imaan walo ! apni fikr karo. jab tum raahe-raast par chal rahey ho to jo shakhs gumrah hai us sey tumhen koi nuqsan nahin."" unhoney farmaya : tum ney ye masla khabar rakhney waley sey puchha hai. mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey is barey mein daryaft kiya tha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : balke eik doosrey ko neki ka hukm do aur eik doosrey ko burai sey mana karo yahan tak key jab to dekhey ke bukhl ka hukm maana jata hai (har shakhs bukhl kar raha hai goya bukhl ki hukumat hai), khahish ki perwi ki jati hai, duniya ko tarjeeh di jati hai, aur har shakhs ko apni raaey hi achchhi lagti hai, aur terey samney aisi soorate-haal aa jaey ke to uska muqabla nahin kar sakta to phir khas apni jaan ki fikr kar aur Awam ki fikr chhod dey kyonkey tumharey aagey sabr ka zamana aa raha hai. us daur mein sabr (aur haq par qaaim rehna) is tarah (dushwaar) hoga jaisey angaarey ko mutthi mein lena. un dinon mein (sahih nek) amal karney waley ko aam halaat mein yehi amal karney waley pachas aadmiyon key barabar sawab milega."
4015,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, arz kiya gaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum (musalman) kab neki ka hukm dena aur burai sey mana karna chhod baitheingey? aap ney farmaya : jab tumharey andar wo (kharaabiyaan) zahir ho jaeyn jo tum sey pehli qomon mein zahir hui thin. hamney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! hum sey pehli ummaton mein kya zahir huwa tha? aap ney farmaya : hukumat kam umr (ya bachkaana zehen rakhney waley) afrad mein aur be-hayai badon mein (jawan to bad-kaari mein mulawwis hongey hi, boodhey bhi baaz nahin aayengey) aur ilm tumharey zaleel logon mein. Hazrat Zaid bin Yahyaa (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : tumharey zaleel logon mein ilm honey, ka matlab ye hai ke ilm fasiq (aur bad kirdaar) logon mein hoga (jo ilm par amal nahin kerengey)."
4016,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : momin key liye munasib nahin ke apney aap ko zaleel kerey. Sahaba ney arz kiya : apney aap ko kaisey zaleel kar sakta hai? aap ney farmaya : aisi aazmaaish mein na padey jis mein pura utarney ki taqat nahin."
4017,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala qiyamat key din bandey sey sawal kerega yahan tak key ye bhi farmaeyga : jab tu ney burai dekhi thi to us sey mana kyon nahin kiya tha? phir jab (wo jawab na dey sakeyga to) Allah bandey ko jawab sikha dega, wo kaheyga : ya Allah ! mujhey tujh sey (rehmat ki) ummid thi aur bandon sey dar lagta tha."
4018,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala zalim ko mohlat deta hai, phir jab usey pakadta hai to chhodta nahin. phir aap ney ye aayat padhi : (وَكَذَلِكَ أَخْذُ رَبِّكَ إِذَاۤ اَخَذَ الْقُرٰي وَ هِيَ ظَالِمَةٌ),''aap key parwardigar ki pakad ka yehi tariqa hai jab wo bastiyon key rehney waley zalimon ko pakadta hai.''"
4019,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamari taraf mutawajjeh ho kar farmaya : aey muhaajiron ki jamaat ! paanch cheezen aisi hain ke jab tum un mein mubtala ho gaey (to un ki saza zarur milegi) aur main Allah ki panah maangta hun ke wo (buri cheezen) tum tak pahunchein : jab bhi kisi qom mein be-hayai (bad-kaari waghera) elania honey lagti hai to un mein taaoon aur aisi beemaariyaan phel jati hain jo unkey guzrey huye buzurgon mein nahin hoti thin. jab bhi wo naap-tol mein kami kartey hain, in ko qehat saali, rozgar ki tangi aur badshah key zulm key zariey sey saza di jati hai. jab wo apney maalon ki zakat dena band kartey hain to un sey aasman ki barish rok li jati hai. agar janwer na hon to unhen kabhi barish na miley. jab wo Allah aur uskey Rasool ka ehad todtey hain to un par dusri qomon mein sey dushman musallat kar diye jatey hain, wo un sey wo kuchh chhin letey hain jo unkey haath mein hota hai. jab bhi unkey Imam (sardar aur leedar) Allah key qanoon key mutabiq faisley nahin kartey aur jo Allah ney utara hai usey ikhtiyar nahin kartey to Allah Taala un mein aapas ki ladaai dal deta hai."
4020,"Hazrat Abu-Malik Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri ummat key kuchh log sharab piyen gey. wo uska koi aur naam rakh leingey. in ko gaaney waliyan saaz baja kar gaaney sunaeyngi. Allah Taala unhen zamin mein dhansa dega aur un mein sey baaz ko bandar aur khinzir bana dega."
4021,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (Allah taala key qol) : (یَلْعَنُهُمُ اللّٰهُ وَ یَلْعَنُهُمُ اللّٰعِنُوْنَۙ),''un par Allah lanat karta hai aur un par lanat bhejney waley lanat bhejtey hain.'' (ki baabat) farmaya : (lanat bhejney walon sey murad), zamin key chopaey hain."
4022,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sirf neki umr mein izafa karti hai. aur sirf dua hi taqdir ko palat'ti hai. aur insan (baaz oqaat) eik gunah karta hai aur uski wajeh sey rizq sey mehroom ho jata hai."
4023,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! sab sey sakht musibat kis par aati hai? aap ney farmaya : nabiyon par, phir jo unkey baad sab sey afzal hain, phir jo unkey baad afzal hain. bandey par uskey Deen key mutabiq aazmaaish aati hai. agar wo apney Deen (aur emaan) mein mazbut ho to uski aazmaaish bhi sakht hoti hai. agar uska eman naram ho to uskey eman key mutabiq aazmaaish aati hai. bandey par aazmaaish (aur musibat) aati rehti hai yahan tak key usey aisa kar key chhodti hai ke wo zamin par chal phir raha hota hai aur is par koi gunah (baqi) nahin hota."
4024,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa jabkey aap ko bukhar tha. mainey aap key jism Mubarak par haath rakha to lihaaf key ooper rakhey huye merey haath ko haraarat mehsus hui. mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! aap ko kitna sakht bukhar hai ! aap ney farmaya : hum (anbiya) isi tarah hotey hain ke hamen musibat (ya aazmaesh) bhi dugni aati hai aur sawab bhi dugna milta hai. mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! sab sey ziyada sakht aazmaaish kin logon ko aati hai? aap ney farmaya : nabiyon ko. mainey kaha : unkey baad ? farmaya : nek logon ko. unhen faqr (ghareebi) key zariey sey aazmaya jata tha yahan tak key (baaz oqaat) eik aadmi ko sirf eik chadar muyassar hoti thi jisey wo jism par lapet leta tha. aur wo musibat par is tarah khush hotey they jis tarah tum rahat par khush hotey ho."
4025,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : goya main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekh raha hun ke aap kisi Nabi ki haalat bayan farma rahey hain : usey uski qom ney maara, wo apney chehrey sey khoon saaf kartey they aur kehtey they : merey Rab ! meri qom ko maaf kar dey, wo jantey nahin."
4026,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hum Hazrat Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) sey ziyada shak karney ka haq rakhtey hain jab unhoney farmaya : (رَبِّ اَرِنِیْ كَیْفَ تُحْیِ الْمَوْتٰی . . . . . .), ''merey Rab ! mujhey dikha to mardon ko kaisey zinda kerega? Allah Taala ney farmaya : kya to eman nahin laya? Ibrahim ney kaha : kyon nahin ? lekin (sawal isliye kiya hai) ta ke mera dil mutmain ho jaey. aur Allah Taala Hazrat Loot (Alaihissalam) par reham farmaaey ! wo mazbut saharey ki panah ley rahey they. aur agar main qaid mein itna arsa rehta jitna arsa Hazrat Yusuf (Alaihissalam) rahey to main bulaney waley ki baat maan leta.''"
4027,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke jang uhad mein jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka daant shaheed huwa, chehra Mubarak zakhmi huwa aur khoon aap key chehre-Mubarak sey bahney laga to aap chehre-Mubarak sey khoon poonchhtey they aur farmatey they : ye qom kaisey najat paeygi jisney apney Nabi key chehrey ko khoon aalud kar diya, jabke wo in ko Allah ki taraf bula raha tha? is par Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil farmaai : (لَیْسَ لَكَ مِنَ الْأَمْرَ شَيْءٌ),''aey Peghambar ! aap key ikhtiyar mein kuchh nahin (Allah chahey to un ki tauba qubul farma ley, aur chahey to unhen azab dey kyonkey wo zalim hain).''"
4028,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, eik din Jibril (Alaihissalam) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas tashrif laye to aap bahut ghamgin bethey huye they. Makka key baaz logon ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par eent phaik kar key lahu-luhaan kar diya tha. Jibril ney kaha : kya baat hai? aap ney farmaya : un logon ney merey sath ye ye zulm kiya hai. Jibril (Alaihissalam) ney farmaya : kya aap chahtey hain ke aap ko eik nishani dikhaoon? aap ney farmaya : haan dikhaaiye. unhoney wadi ki dusri taraf eik darkht ki taraf dekh kar kaha is darkht ko bulaiye. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isey bulaya to wo chal kar aaya aur aap key samney khada ho gaya. Jibril (Alaihissalam) ney kaha : usey kahey wapis chala jaey. aap ney isey kaha to wo wapis ho gaya yahan tak key apni jagah par chala gaya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey kafi hai."
4029,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey wo sab log shumar kar do jinhoney Islam ka kalima padha hai. hamney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kya aap ko hamarey barey mein khof hai jabke hamari tadaad chhe aur saat-sau key darmiyan hai? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhen nahin maloom, shayad tum par aazmaaish aaye. Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : phir hum par aazmaaish aai yahan tak key hum chhup-chhup kar namazein padhney lagey."
4030,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey bayan kartey hain ke jis raat Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Meraj hui, aap ko (safar Meraj key doran main eik jagah) umda khushbu mehsus hui. aap ney farmaya : Jibril ! ye umda khushbu kaisi hai? unhoney farmaya : ye Maashta ki, unkey do beton ki aur unkey shohar ki qabron ki khushbu hai. unhoney farmaya : unka waqiyaaa yun hai ke Hazrat Khizr (Alaihissalam) Bani-Israel key moazziz afrad mein sey they. wo (apney kaam kaaj key silsiley mein) eik raahib key paas sey guzartey jo apney ibadat khaney mein hota tha. wo unhen dekhta to unhein Islam ki taalim deta. jab Khizr (Alaihissalam) jawan huye to unkey walid ney eik aurat sey un ki shaadi kar di. Khizr (Alaihissalam) ney usey (Islam ki) taalim di aur us sey wada liya ke kisi ko nahin bataaeygi. wo aurton key qarib nahin jatey they. unhoney us aurat ko Talaq dey di. unkey walid ney eik aur aurat sey un ki shaadi kar di. unhoney usey bhi (Islam ki) taalim di aur us sey wada liya ke wo kisi ko nahin bataeygi. un mein sey eik aurat ney to raz rakha jabkey dusri ney zahir kar diya. wo (watan sey) bhag gaey yahan tak key samandar main eik jazeerey mein ja pahunchey. (wahan) do aadmi endhan jama karney aaye. unhoney Khizr (Alaihissalam) ko dekh liya. un mein sey eik ney raz rakha, doosrey ney zahir kar diya. usney kaha : mainey Khizr ko dekha hai. us sey puchha gaya : terey sath aur kis ney dekha hai? usney kaha : falan ney. us sey puchha gaya to usney raaz chhupa liya. unkey yahan ye qanoon tha ke jo shakhs jhoot boley, usey qatl kar diya jaey. us (chhipaaney waley) ney chhipaaney wali aurat sey shaadi kar li. wo Firon ki beti ko kanghi kar rahi thi ke kanghi (uskey haath sey) gir gaee. usney kaha : Firon ka bura ho. usney apney baap ko bataya. us aurat (Maashta kanghi karney wali) ka khawind bhi tha aur do betey they. Firon ney unhen bulwa liya. usney un miyan biwi ko Deen sey pherney ki koshish ki. unhoney inkar kar diya. usney kaha : main tumhen qatl kar dunga. unhoney kaha : agar to hamein qatl karey to hum par ye ehsan karna ke hamein eik jagah dafn karna. usney aisey hi kya.  jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Meraj hui to aap ko umda khushbu mehsus hui. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Jibreel (Alaihissalam) sey daryaft kiya to unhoney ye baat sunai."
4031,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ziyada sawab badi aazmaaish ka hota hai. Allah Taala jab kisi qom sey mohabbat karta hai to un par aazmaaish daalta hai. jo razi rahey usey raza milegi, aur jo naraz ho, usey narazi hasil hogi."
4032,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo momin logon sey milta julta hai aur un sey milney wali takleef par sabr karta hai, wo us momin sey ziyada sawab hasil kar leta hai jo logon sey milta julta nahin aur un ki taraf sey aaney wali takleef par sabr nahin karta."
4033,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen khubiyan jis mein hon, usey eman ka lutf hasil hota hai. eik riwayat mein hai : usey eman ki mithaas hasil ho jati hai. (pehli khoobi) aur jab usey Allah ney kufr sey najat dey di ho to usey dobara kufr ikhtiyar karney sey aag mein dala jana ziyada pasand ho. (doosri) kisi shakhs sey mohabbat aur dosti rakhey to mehaz Allah key liye rakhey. (teesri) uskey dil mein Allah aur uskey Rasool ki mohabbat baqi sab ki mohabbat sey badh kar ho."
4034,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mujh sey merey jigri dost jaani mehbub (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney nasihat kartey huye farmaya : Allah key sath kisi chiz ko shareek na karna, chahey tujhey tukdey tukdey kar diya jaey ya tujhey jala diya jaey. aur farz namaz jaan boojh kar tarak na karna. jisney isey amadan tarak kiya, us sey (Allah ki hifazat ka) zimma jata raha. aur sharab na peena kyonkey wo har burai ki chaabi hai."
4035,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : duniya mein sirf aazmaaish aur fitna hi baqi reh gaya hai."
4036,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : anqarib logon par dhokey sey bhar-poor saal ayengey. un mein jhootey ko sachcha samjha jaeyga aur sachchey ko jhoota kaha jaeyga. bad-dayanat ko amanat daar samjha jaeyga aur diyanat daar ko bad diyanat kaha jaeyga. aur رُوَیْبِضَہ baaten kerengey, kaha gaya : رُوَیْبِضَہ (ka matlab) kya hai? aap ney farmaya : haqeer aadmi Awam key maamlat mein raaey dega."
4037,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! duniya khatam nahin hogi yahan tak key (ye nobat aa jaeygi ke) aadmi kisi qabr key paas sey guzreyga to is par gir padeyga aur kaheyga : kaash ! main is qabr waley ki jagah (mar kar dafn ho chuka) hota. wo Deen (key barey mein pesh aaney wali mushkilat) ki wajeh sey aisey nahin karega balke (dunyawi) mushkilat ki wajeh sey karega."
4038,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum is tarah chun liye jaogey jis tarah nikammi aur raddi khajuron mein sey (umda) khajuren chun (kar utha) li jati hain. achchhey log (duniya sey) chaley jaeyngey aur burey log reh jaeyngey, isliye agar tum sey ho sakey to mar jana."
4039,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : maamla hamesha sakht sey sakht hota chala jaeyga. duniya peechhey hat'ti chali jaeygi. logon mein bukhl hi ziyada hota jaeyga. qiyamat mehaz bad tareen logon par qaaim hogi aur Esa ibne Maryam (Aleh.) key siwa koi Mehdi nahin."
4040,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main aur qiyamat is tarah bhejey gaey hain. aur aap ney apni dono ungliyon ko jama farmaya."
4041,"Hazrat Huzefa bin Usaid Ghifaari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney baalaai kamrey sey jhank kar hamein dekha jabke hum qiyamat key barey mein baaten kar rahey they. aap ney farmaya : qiyamat nahin aayegi jab tak das nishaniyan zahir na ho jaeyn : Dajjaal, Dhuwan aur suraj ka maghrib sey tulu hona."
4042,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : ghazwaae-tabuk key doran mein, main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa. aap chamdey key eik khemey mein tashrif farma they. main khemey key samney beth gaya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Auf ! andar aa jaao. mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! sara hi aa jaaun. aap ney farmaya : sarey hi (aa jaao). phir farmaya : Auf ! yad rakho, qiyamat sey pehley chhe waqiyat (pesh aaney waley) hain : un mein sey eik meri wafat hai. (ye sun kar gham aur pareshani ki wajeh sey) main bolney key qabil na raha (hakka, bakaa reh gaya). Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kaho (ye) eik (alamat hai), phir Baitul-Maqdis ki Fateh, phir tumharey andar aisi bimari pheleygi jis key zariey sey Allah Taala tumhen aur tumhari aulad ko shahadat ka darja dega aur tumharey aamaal ko paak kar dega, phir tumharey andar maal aur dolat aa jaeygi. (farawani key bawajud hirs bahut hogi) yahan tak key aadmi ko sau Dinar diye jaeyngey, tab bhi wo naraz rahega. aur tumharey andar eik fitna barpa hoga ke wo kisi musalman key ghar mein dakhil huye baghair nahin rahega, phir tumharey darmiyan aur banu-asfar (Romiyon) key darmiyan suleh (jang bandi) hogi. wo tumhen dhoka dengey aur usi jhandon key sath tumhari taraf (hamla karney key liye) aayengey. har jhandey taley baara hazar (fauji) hongey."
4043,"Hazrat Huzefa bin Yamaan (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak key tum apney Imam ko shaheed karogey aur talwaaron key sath (eik doosrey sey) jang karogey. aur burey log tumhari duniya key waris ho jaeyngey."
4044,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) logon key liye (ghar sey) bahar tashrif farma they ke eik aadmi khidmat mein hazir huwa. usney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! qiyamat kab aayegi? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis sey puchha ja raha hai wo us (qiyamat) ki baabat poochhney waley sey ziyada nahin janta lekin main tujhey uski nishaniyan bata deta hun. jab londi apni maalika ko janm dey to ye uski eik alamat hai. jab nangey paon aur nangey badan waley (faqir) logon key raees bin jaeyngey to ye bhi uski eik nishani hai. jab bakriyon key charwahey eik doosrey sey lambi (aur oonchi) imaraten bananey lagen to ye bhi uski eik alamat hai. (qiyamat ka ilm) in paanch chizon mein shamil hai jinhen Allah key siwa koi nahin janta. phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye aayat tilawat farmaai : (اِنَّ اللّهَ عِنْدَهُ عِلْمُ السَّاعَةِ وَ یُنَزِّلُ الْغَیْثَ وَ یَعْلَمُ مَا فِی الْاَرْحَامِ . ۔ . ۔ . ۔ ۔),'be-shak Allah hi key paas qiyamat ka ilm hai, wohi barish nazil farmata hai, aur jo kuchh maaon key peton mein hai usey janta hai, aur koi nahin janta ke wo kal kya kuchh kerega, na kisi ko ye malum hai ke wo kis zamin mein mareyga. Allah Taala hi purey ilm wala , sahih khabron wala hai.''"
4045,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : kya main tumhen eik hadees sunaun jo mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suni hai, merey baad tumhen wo hadees koi nahin sunaiyega. mainey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad suna : qiyamat ki baaz alaamaten ye hain ke ilm utha liya jaeyga, jihalat phel jaeygi, bad kaari aam ho jaaeygi, sharab (kasrat sey) pi jaaeygi, mard khatam ho jaeyngey aur aurten baqi reh jaaeyngi yahan tak key pachas aurton ki khabar geeri karney wala sirf eik mard hoga."
4046,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak key dariyaaey Faraat sey soney ka eik pahad zahir hoga. log uskey liye aapas mein ladengey aur har das mein sey no afrad qatl ho jaeyngey."
4047,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak key maal bahut ziyada ho jaeyga, aur fitney zahir hongey aur haraj bahut hoga. Sahaba ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! haraj sey kya murad hai? aap ney teen baar farmaya : qatl , qatl , qatl."
4048,"Hazrat Ziyad bin Labid Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kisi waqiey ka zikr kiya aur farmaya : ye ilm chaley janey ka waqt hoga. mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! ilm kaisey uth jaeyga jabke hum Quran padhtey hain, apney beton ko padhatey hain aur hamarey betey apney beton ko padhaaengey? qiyamat tak (isi tarah silsila jari rahega). Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Ziyad ! teri maa tujhey roey, main to tujhey Madiney mein sab sey ziyada samajh daar aadmi khayal karta tha. kya ye Yahudi aur Esai Torat aur Injeel nahin padhtey? lekin wo un mein mojud kisi hukm par amal nahin kartey."
4049,"Hazrat Huzefa bin Yamaan (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Islam is tarah mahaw ho jaaeyga jis tarah kapdey key nuqoosh mit jatey hain yahan tak key logon ko ye bhi malum nahin rahega ke rozey kya hotey hain ya namaz ya qurbani ya sadqa kya hota hai. Allah ki kitab ko eik hi raat mein utha liya jaaeyga aur zamin mein uski eik aayat bhi nahin rahegi. logon mein kuchh boodhey mard aur aurten reh jaaeyngi jo kahengi : hamney apney buzurgon ko (لاَ إِلٰهَ إِلَّا الله) kehtey dekha tha, hum bhi kehtey hain. (Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) key eik shagrid) Hazrat Sila bin Zufr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : unhen (لاَ إِلٰهَ إِلَّا الله) sey kya faaeyda hoga jab unhen namaz , rozey , qurbani aur sadqey ka bhi ilm nahin hoga? Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ney un sey munh pher liya. unhoney teen baar ye sawal kiya aur har dafa Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) un sey munh phertey rahey. teesri baar un ki taraf mutawajjeh ho kar teen baar farmaya : aey Sila ! (is daur mein) yehi unhen jahannam sey bachaleyga."
4050,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat sey pehley aisa zamana aayega jis mein ilm uth jaaeyga aur jihalat phel jaaeygi aur haraj ziyada hoga. aur haraj sey murad qatl aur gharat hai."
4051,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumharey aagey (mustaqbil mein) aisa zamana aayega jis mein jihalat phel jaaeygi, ilm uth jaaeyga, aur haraj ziyada hoga. Sahaba ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! haraj kya hota hai? aap ney farmaya : qatl aur gharat."
4052,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : zamana qarib ho jaeyga, ilm kam ho jaeyga, harisaana, bukhl aam ho jaeyga, fitney zahir hongey aur haraj bahut ziyada ho jaeyga. Sahaba ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! haraj kya hai? aap ney farmaya : qatl."
4053,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein do baaten batai thin. in dono mein sey eik to mainey dekh li (ke wo waqey (zaahir) ho gaee hai) aur dusri (key waqey honey) ka mujhey intizar hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : amanat (diyanat daari ki sift) logon key dilon ki gehraai mein utri------. (hadees key Raavi Ali bin Muhammad) Tanaafusi ney kaha : (جَذْرِ قُلُوبِ الرِّجَالِ) sey murad, (وَسْطَ قُلُوبِ الرِّجَالِ) hai, yani dil key darmiyan mein . . . aur Quran nazil huwa, hamney Quran bhi seekha aur sunnat bhi seekhi (chunanche ye khoobi mazeed pukhta ho gaee). phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein uskey uth jaaney key barey mein bayan kiya aur farmaya : aadmi eik baar soeyga to amanat uskey dil sey uth jaaeygi, uska eik nishan reh jaaeyga, jaisey eik nuqtey ka nishan. phir wo soeyga to (baaqi bachi hui) amanat bhi uskey dil sey uth jaaeygi, to uska asar eik aabley ki tarah reh jaaeyga, jaisey terey paon par angaara gir padey aur wo phool jaaey. tujhey wo ubhraa huwa nazar aata hai, halanke uskey andar kuchh nahin hota. (ye kehtey huye) Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ney mutthi bhar kankariyaan ley kar apni pindli par giraaeen. aap (Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) ney farmaya : phir log eik doosrey sey lein den kya kerengey aur koi bhi amanat ada nahin kerega yahan tak key kaha jaeyga : falan qabiley main eik diyanat daar aadmi bhi hai. aur yahan tak key eik aadmi key barey mein kaha jaeyga : wo kitna aql mand hai ! kitna baa-himmat hai ! kitna samajh-daar hai ! halanke uskey dil mein raai key eik daney jitna bhi eman nahin hoga. aur (Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : ) mujh par eik waqt wo tha ke mujhey kisi sey lain-dain karney mein koi parwah nahin hoti thi. (mujhey yaqin hota tha ke) agar wo musalman hai to uska eman usey merey paas (mera haq ada karney key liye) wapis ley aayega, aur agar wo Yahudi ya Esai hai to uska aamil (zimmedar) usey merey paas ley aayega. lekin aaj to (ye haalat hai ke) main falan aur falan key siwa kisi sey kharid aur farokht nahin karta."
4054,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala jab kisi aadmi ko tabah karna chahta hai to us sey haya ko cheen leta hai. aur jab us sey hayaa cheen leta hai to tujhey wo shakhs na-pasandida aur qabile-nafrat mehsus hota hai. jab wo naa-pasandida aur qabile-nafrat ho jata hai to us sey diyanat-daari chhin li jati hai. jab us sey diyanat-daari chhin jati hai to usey khayanat karne wala aur khayanat mein mashhoor dekhta hai. jab wo khayanat aur khayanat mein mashhoor ho jata hai to us sey reham dili chhin jati hai. jab us sey reham dili chhin jati hai to to usey laa'nati aur logon sey is par laa'naten padti dekhta hai. jab to usey laa'nati dekhey aur is par laa'naten pad rahi hon to uski gardan sey Islam ka qalaada utar jata hai."
4055,"Hazrat Abu-Sareeha (Huzaifa bin Usaid Ghifaari) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : hum log qiyamat key barey mein baaten kar rahey they ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney baala khaney sey jhaankaa aur farmaya : qiyamat nahin aayegi jab tak das nishaniyan zahir na ho jaeyn : suraj ka maghrib sey tulu hona, Dajjaal, dhuwan, daabbatul-arz , Yajuj Majuj , Hazrat Esa ibne Maryam (Aleh.) ka zuhoor (nuzool), aur zamin mein dhans janey key teen waqiyat : eik mashriq mein, eik maghrib mein aur eik jazeera Arab mein. aur (Yamen key shehar) Adn Abyan ki gehraai sey eik aag ka zuhoor jo logon ko haank kar hashr key maidan mein ley aayegi. jab wo raat ko thehrengey to wo (aag) bhi unkey sath thehreygi. jab wo dophare ko (aaram key liye) qailula kerengey to wo bhi unkey sath qailula kereygi."
4056,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : chhe chizon sey pehley pehley amal kar lo : suraj ka maghrib sey tulu hona , dhuwan , daabbatul-arz (zameen ka jaanwer), Dajjaal, aadmi ka zaati masla (maut) aur aam logon ka maamla (umoomi fitna)."
4057,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (qiyamat ki) nishaniyan do sau saal key baad zahir hongi."
4058,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri ummat key paanch tabqey hongey : chaalis saal tak neki aur taqwe waley log hongey, phir un sey muttasil (lage hue) eik sau bees saal eik doosrey par reham karney waley aur mail milaap rakhney waley log hongey, phir un sey muttasil eik sau saath saal tak eik doosrey sey naraz rehney waley aur qata' talluq karney waley log hongey , phir uskey baad qatl aur gharat hogi, bach jana ! bach jana ! dusri sanad sey Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri ummat key paanch tabqey hain : har tabqaa chaalis saal ka hai. mera aur merey sathiyon ka taqaa ilm aur eman walon ka hai. doosra tabqa san chaalis sey san assi tak neki aur taqwe walon ka hai. phir Raavi ney mazkura riwayat key hum maana hadees bayan ki."
4059,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat sey pehley (insanon ki) soorten badleingi, wo zamin mein dhasengey aur un par patthar barsengey."
4060,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna, aap farma rahey they : meri ummat key aakhir mein zamin mein dhasney, soorten bigad janey aur patthar barasney key waqiyat hongey."
4061,"Hazrat Nafey (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, eik aadmi Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) key paas aaya aur usney kaha : falan shakhs ney aap ko salam kaha hai. Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mujhey khabar mili hai ke us shakhs ney bidat ikhtiyar ki hai. agar usney waaqaee bidat ikhtiyar ki hai to usey meri taraf sey salam na kehna. mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huye suna hai : meri ummat mein ya (aap ney farmaya : ) is ummat mein soorten bigad janey, zamin mein dhasney aur patthar barasney key waqiyat hongey. Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : ye taqdir (ka inkar kerney) walon mein hongey."
4062,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri ummat mein zamin mein dhasne, soorten bigadne aur patthar barasney key waqiyat hongey."
4063,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : eik lashkar Baitullah par hamla karney key liye uski taraf aayega yahan tak key jab wo Bedaa mein pahuncheingey to lashkar ka darmiyani hissa zamin mein dhansa diya jaeyga. unkey aagey waley apney peechhey walon ko aawazen dengey to unhen bhi dhansa diya jaaeyga. un mein sey sirf eik aadmi bhag kar bacheyga jis sey dusron ko us waqiye ka ilm hoga. (Hazrat Abdullah bin Safwan (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya :  (jab Hujjaaj ka lashkar) Makka par hamla karney key liye (aaya to hamney guman kiya ke ye wohi log hain) jinka zikr is hadees mein hai. (eik aadmi ney) ye hadees sun kar Abdullah bin Safwan (Raziallahu anhuma) sey) kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke aap ney Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) par jhoot nahin bola aur Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf (apney paas sey bana kar) jhooti baat mansub nahin ki."
4064,"Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : log is Kaabe par hamley karney sey baaz nahin aayengey yahan tak key eik lashkar hamla-aawar hoga. jab wo maqame-bedaa par ya banjar maidan mein pahuncheingey to unkey aagey aur peechhey walon ko zamin nigal legi aur darmiyan waley bhi najat nahin paaeyngey. mainey arz kiya : agar un mein koi aisa shakhs huwa jisey zabardasti laya gaya ho to? aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala unhen un niyaton key mutabiq uthaeyga jo unkey dilon mein thin."
4065,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us lashkar ka zikr farmaya jisey dhansa diya jaeyga. Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! shayad un mein koi aisa shakhs bhi ho jisey jabr sey laya gaya ho. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : unhen un ki niyaton key mutabiq uthaya jaaeyga."
4066,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (daabbatul-arz) zahir hoga to uskey paas Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Dawud (Aleh.) ki anguthi hogi aur Hazrat Musa bin Imran (Aleh.) ka aasa hoga. wo aasey key sath momin key chehrey ko roshan kar dega aur anguthi key sath kafir ki naak par nishan laga dega yahan tak key mahalley key log jama hongey to (eik doosrey ko is tarah mukhatib kerengey ke) ye kaheyga : aey momin ! aur wo kaheyga : aey kafir ! (Imam Ibne-Maja key shagrid) Abul-Hasan Qataan ney (apni oonchi sanad sey bhi) is sey milti jhulti hadees bayan ki hai. aur is main eik martaba farmaya : to ye kaheyga : aey momin ! aur ye (kaheyga : ) aey kafir !"
4067,"Hazrat Barida bin Haseeb Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mujhey Makka key qarib dehat main eik jagah ley gaey. dekha to wo khushk zamin thi jis key ird-gird ret thi. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : daabbatul-arz (zameen ka jaanwer), us jagah sey niklega. mainey dekha ke wo jagah eik baalisht lambi aur paun baalisht chodi thi. Hazrat Abdullah bin Barida (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : is sey kaee saal baad mainey Haj kiya to wo jagah merey is aasey ki pemaaish key sath itni itni (wasee (lambi-chaudi)) ho chuki thi. (Abdullah key shagrid farmatey hain : ) ye kehtey waqt Abdullah ney hamein apna aasaa dikhaya."
4068,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat nahin aayegi jab tak suraj maghrib sey tulu na ho. jab wo tulu hoga aur log usey (maghrib sey tulu hota) dekhengey to zamin par mojud tamam log eman ley ayengey. us waqt kisi ko eman laney sey faeyda nahin hoga. jo pehley eman nahin laya hoga."
4069,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sab sey pehley zahir honey wali alamat suraj ka maghrib sey tulu hona aur zuhaa (chaasht) key waqt logon key samney daabba (jaanwer) ka zahir hona hai. Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : un mein sey jo alamat bhi pehley zahir hui, dusri us sey qarib hogi. Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : merey khayal mein suraj ka maghrib sey tulu hona ( daabba key zuhoor sey) pehley hoga."
4070,"Hazrat Safwan bin Assaal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : suraj ghurub honey ki samt main eik khula huwa darwaza hai jiski chaurai sattar saal (mein tey honey wala fasla) hai. wo darwaza tauba key liye khula rahega yahan tak key suraj uski taraf sey tulu ho. jab wo udhar sey tulu ho gaya to kisi aisey shakhs ko eman sey faeyda nahin hoga jo is sey pehley eman nahin la chuka hoga ya jisney eman la kar neki nahin ki hogi."
4071,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Dajjaal baain aankh sey kaanaa hai. ziyada baalon wala hai. uskey sath jannat aur jahannam hogi. uski jahannam (asal mein) baagh hogi aur uski jannat (asal mein) aag hogi."
4072,"Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hum sey hadees bayan kartey huye farmaya : Dajjaal mashriq ki eik zamin sey niklega, usey Khuraasaan kaha jata hai. kuchh log uska ittiba kerengey, unkey chehrey aisey hongey jaisey teh daar dhaal hoti hai."
4073,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey mujh sey ziyada kisi ney Dajjaal key barey mein nahin poochha. aap ney mujh sey farmaya : to uskey barey mein kya poochhtey hai? mainey kaha : log kehtey hain ke uskey sath khaney peeney ka saman hoga. aap ney farmaya : wo Allah ki nazar mein us sey ziyada haqeer hai."
4074,"Hazrat Fatima binte Qais (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaz ada karney key baad member par tashrif farma huye, halanke is sey pehley aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sirf Juma key din (khutba Juma key liye) member par tashrif rakhtey they. logon ko is sey pareshani hui. koi khada tha, koi betha tha. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney haath sey ishara farmaya ke beth jao. (phir farmaya : ) Allah ki qism ! is jagah mein koi aisi targheeb aur daraane wali baat bataaney khada nahin huwa jis sey tumhen faeyda ho. lekin merey paas Tameem Daari aaye aur mujhey eik khabar di jis sey mujhey itni khushi hui ke mujhey dophare ko khushi aur aakhon ki thandak ki wajeh sey neend nahin aai, isliye mainey chaha ke tumharey Nabi ki khushi sey tum sab ko aagah kar dun. mujhey Tameem Daari key eik chacha zaad ney bataya ke (samandari safar key doran mein) mukhalif hawa unhen eik ghair maroof jazeerey tak ley gaee. wo jahaz ki kashtiyon mein beth kar jazeerey mein pahunchey. unhen badi badi palkon wali eik siyah faam chiz mili. unhoney usey kaha : to kon hai? usney kaha : main Jass'sasa hun. unhoney kaha : hamein (wazahat sey) bata. usney kaha : main na tumhen kuchh bataungi, na tum sey kuchh poochhungi. lekin ye mandir jo tumhen nazar aa raha hai, is mein jao. wahan eik aadmi hai jiski shadeed khahish hai ke tum usey kuchh batao aur wo tumhen kuchh bataey. wo us mandir mein gaey aur us shakhs key paas ja pahunchey, dekha to eik badi umr ka aadmi hai jo khub jakdaa huwa hai. us sey bahut ranj aur gham zahir ho raha hai, bahut haaye-waaey kar raha hai. usney un sey kaha : kahan sey aaye ho? unhoney kaha : Sham sey. usney kaha : Arbon ka kya haal hai? wo boley : hum Arab key log hain, to kis chiz key barey mein poochhta hai? usney kaha : tumharey andar jo aadmi ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) zahir huwa hai uska kya haal hai? wo boley : achchha haal hai. us (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) ney qom ka muqabla kiya to Allah ney usey qom par ghalba ata farma diya. ab wo sab (ehale-Arab) muttahid hain. unka mabood bhi eik hai aur Deen bhi eik hai. usney kaha : zaghar key chashmey ka kya haal hai? unhoney kaha : achchha hai. log us sey kheti ko pani detey aur khud peeney key liye pani bhartey hain. usney kaha : beesaan aur amaan key darmiyan key khajuron key darakhton ka kya haal hai? unhoney kaha : har saal phal detey hain. usney kaha : buhira tabriya ka kya haal hai? unhoney kaha : uska pani itna ziyada hai ke kinaron sey uchhalta hai. usney teen baar thandi saans li, phir bola : agar main is qaid sey chhoot gaya to zamin ka koi ilaaqa nahin rahega jis par merey ye qadam na lagen, siwaye Tayiba key. is par mera bas nahin chaleyga. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye sun kar meri khushi ki inteha ho gaee (behad khushi hui). ye (Madina Munawra hi) Tayiba hai. qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! iskey har tang aur khuley raastey par, har maidan aur pahad par qiyamat tak key liye farishtey talwaarein soontey khadey hain."
4075,"Hazrat Nawaas bin Samaan Kilaabi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, eik subah Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Dajjaal ka zikr farmaya, uski hiqaarat ka zikr farmaya aur uska azeem (bada fitna) hona bayan farmaya. (ya matlab ye hai ke tafsil sey bayan kartey huye kabhi mamool ki aawaz mein bayan farmaya , kabhi aawaz buland farmaai) yahan tak key hamein mehsus huwa ke wo khajoor key darakhton key kisi jhund mein hai (aur abhi nikalney wala hai), jab hum (iskey baad) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye to aap ney hamari ye (khof zadgi ki) kaifiyat mulaahiza farmaai. aap ney farmaya : tum logon ko kya huwa? hamney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! aaj subah aap ney Dajjaal ka zikr farmaya. uski pasti aur bulandi ka zikr farmaya (ya aahista aur buland aawaz sey tanbih farmaai) yahan tak key hamein mehsus huwa ke wo khajuron key jhund mein hai. aap ney farmaya : mujhey tumharey barey mein Dajjaal sey ziyada kisi aur chiz sey khatra hai. agar wo us waqt zahir huwa jabke main tumharey andar mojud hun to tum sey pehley main uska muqabla kar lunga (dalaeel key zariey sey ho ya uskey shodon (fareb) ki haqiqat zahir kar key ho) aur agar wo us waqt zahir huwa jab main tumharey andar nahin hunga to har shakhs apna difaa khud kerega aur meri adam (ghair) mojudgi mein Allah har musalman ka madadgar hai. Dajjaal ghungariyaaley baalon wala jawan hai. uski aankh ubhri hui hai. wo aisa hai ke main usey Abdul-Uzzaa bin Qatan sey tashbih deta hun. tum mein sey jo koi usey dekhey uskey samney Sura Kahaf ki ibtidaai aayaat padhey. wo Sham aur Iraaq key darmiyan eik raastey par zahir hoga aur daain baain fasad phelaeyga. Allah key bando ! Sabit qadam rehna. hamney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! wo zamin mein kitna arsa rahega? aap ney farmaya : chaalis din (jinmein sey) eik din eik saal key barabar hoga. eik din eik mahiney key barabar, eik din eik Juma (saat din) key barabar, aur baqi (saintees) din tumharey (aam) dino ki tarah hongey. hamney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! wo din jo saal key barabar hoga, kya us din mein hamein eik din ki (sirf paanch) namazein kafi hongi? aap ney farmaya is din mein uski miqdaar key mutabiq andaza kar lena. hamney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! zamin mein us (key safar kerney) ki raftaar kitni hogi? farmaya : jaisey badal, jis key peechhey hawa lagi hui ho (aur usey udaey liye ja rahi ho). Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo kuchh logon key paas aayega, unhein (apni baat taslim karney ki) dawat dega, wo uski baat maan leingey aur) uskey dawey ko sachcha maan kar) is par eman ley ayengey. wo aasman ko hukm dega ke barish barsaaey to barish ho jaeygi. zamin ko hukm dega ke faslen ugaey to wo uga degi. unkey maweshi Sham ko (char-chug kar) wapis aayengey to un ki kauhaanein intehai oonchi, unkey than intehai badey (doodh sey labrez) aur un ki kokhein khub nikli hui hongi (khoob sair hongey). phir wo kuchh (aur) logon key paas jaaeyga, unhein (apney da'wey par eman laney ki) dawat dega, wo uski baat thukraa dengey, wo unkey paas sey chala jaeyga. subah hogi to wo log qehat ka shikar ho jaaeyngey, unkey paas (maal, janwer waghera) kuchh nahin rahega. phir wo eik khandar par sey guzreyga to usey kaheyga : apney khazaney nikal dey. (fauran zamin mein madfun (daba hua)) wo (khazaney) shehad ki makkhiyon ki tarah uskey peechhey chal padengey. phir wo eik bharpur jawani waley eik aadmi ko bulaeyga aur usey talwaar key eik waar sey do tukdey kar dega. (un tukdon ko eik doosrey sey itni door phenk dega) jitni door teer jata hai. phir usey bulaeyga to wo (zinda ho kar) hanstaa huwa aa jaaeyga, uska chehra (khushi sey) damak raha hoga. isi beech mein Allah Taala Hazrat Esa ibne Mariyam (Aleh.) ko (zameen par) bhej dega. wo dimashq key mashriq ki taraf safed meenaar key qarib nazil hongey, unhoney waras aur za'fraan sey rangey huye do kapdey pehan rakhey hongey, do farishton key paron par haath rakhey huye hongey. jab sar jhkaaeyn gey to (pani key) qatrey tapkeyngey, jab sar uthaeyngey to motiyon ki tarah qatrey girengey. jis kafir tak unkey saans ki mahak pahuncheygi, wo zarur mar jaaeyga. unkey saans ki mahak wahan tak pahuncheygi jahan tak un ki nazar pahuncheygi. phir wo (Dajjaal key taaqqub mein) rawana hongey hattaa key usey lood shehar key darwazey par ja leingey aur qatl kar dengey. phir Allah key Nabi Esa (Alaihissalam) un logon key paas aayengey jinhen Allah ney (Dajjaal key fitney mein mubtala ho kar gumrah honey sey) bacha liya hoga. unkey chehron sey ghubar saaf kerengey aur unhein jannat mein unkey darjaat sey aagah kerengey. isi beech mein Allah Taala Hazrat Esa par wahi nazil farmaeyga : aey Esa ! mainey apney kuchh bandey zahir kiye hain, un sey jang karney ki kisi mein taqat nahin, in (mominon) ko hifazat key liye, ""Toor"" par ley jaaiye. tab Allah Taala Yajuj aur Majuj ko chhod dega. aur wo jaisa ke Allah ney farmaya : har tiley sey (utar-utar kar) bhagey aa rahey hongey. unkey pehley logon (hujoom key shuru key hissey) ka guzar buhira tabriya sey hoga, wo uska saara pani pi jaeyngey. jab unkey pichhley afrad guzrengey to kahengey : kabhi is maqam par pani bhi hota tha. Allah key Nabi Esa (Alaihissalam) aur unkey sathi (Toor hi par) mojud hongey. Yajuj Majuj ki wajeh sey kahin aa ja nahin sakengey isliye khurak ki shadeed qillat ho jaaeygi (yahan tak key unhein eik bail ka sar is sey behtar malum hoga jitna tumhen aaj kal sau asharfiyon ki raqam achchhi lagti hai. Allah key Nabi Esa (Alaihissalam) aur aap key sathi Allah ki taraf tawajjoh farmaeyngey (aur duayen kerengey). tab Allah Yajuj Majuj ki gardanon mein keedey paida kar dega, chunanche wo sarey key sarey eik hi baar mar jaaeyngey. Allah key Nabi Esa (Alaihissalam) aur aap key sathi (pahad sey) utrengey to dekhengey ke eik baalisht jagah bhi aisi nahin jo un ki bad-boo, un ki sadaand aur unkey khoon sey aalooda na ho. wo Allah ki taraf tawajjoh farmaeyngey (aur duayen kerengey) to Allah aisey perindey bhej dega jo bakhti oonton ki gardanon ki tarah hongey. wo un (ki laashon)  ko utha utha kar jahan Allah chahega phenk dengey. phir Allah un par aisi barish nazil farmaeyga jis sey na inton key makaan mein bachao hoga, na khemey mein. wo (barish) zamin ko dho kar aaiyne ki tarah saaf kar degi. phir zamin ko hukm hoga : apney phal uga, aur barkat dobara zahir kar dey. un dino eik jamaat eik anaar khayegi to sab afrad sair ho jaeyngey aur uska chhilka un sab ko saya kar sakeyga. Allah doodh waley janweron mein itni barkat dega ke eik doodh deney wali oontni sey eik badi jamaat ka guzaaraa ho jaeyga. aur eik doodh deney wali gaaey eik qabiley key liye kafi hogi . aur eik doodh deney wali bakri eik badey kunbey ko kafi hogi. wo isi andaz sey (khush-gawaar aur baa barkat din guzar rahey) hongey ke Allah Taala un par eik khush-gawaar hawa bhej dega. wo un ki baghlon key nichey sey guzreygi aur har musalman ki rooh qabz kar leygi. aur baqi aisey log reh jaaeyngey jo is tarah (sare-aam) jima kerengey jis tarah gadhey jufti kartey hain. unhi par qiyamat qaaim hogi. (soor phoonkney par yehi log mareingey)."
4076,"Hazrat Nawaas bin Samaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Yajuj Majuj ki kamanon, teeron aur dhaalon ko musalman saat saal tak endhan key tor par istimal kerengey."
4077,"Hazrat Abu-Umama Baahli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein khutba diya. aap ney khutbey mein ziyada tar Dajjaal key barey mein guftgu farmaai, aur hamein us sey daraya. aap ney us khutbey mein ye bhi farmaya : Allah Taala ney jab sey Adam (Alaihissalam) ki aulad ko paida farmaya hai, zamin mein Dajjaal sey bada fitna zahir nahin huwa. Allah Taala ney jis Nabi ko bhi mab-us farmaya (bheja), usney apni ummat ko Dajjaal sey zarur daraya. main aakhiri Nabi hun aur tum aakhiri ummat ho. wo yaqinan tumharey andar hi zahir hoga. agar wo us waqt zahir huwa jabke main tumharey andar mojud hun to tum sey pehley main uska muqabla kar lunga. aur agar merey baad zahir huwa to har shakhs apna difaa (hifazat) khud kerega. aur meri adam (ghair) mojudgi mein Allah Taala har musalman ka madadgar hai wo Sham aur Iraaq key darmiyan eik raastey par zahir hoga, aur daain baain fasad phelaeyga. Allah key bando ! sabit qadam rehna. main tumhen iski aisi alamaten bataunga jo mujh sey pehley kisi Nabi ney nahin bataeen. wo ibtida (shuruat) mein kaheyga : main Nabi hun, halanke merey baad koi Nabi nahin. phir wo doosra daawey kartey huye kaheyga : main tumhara Rab hun, halanke tum marney sey pehley apney Rab ko nahin dekh saktey. aur wo kaanaa hai aur tumhara Rab kaanaa nahin. uski aakhon key darmiyan (peshani par) kafir likha huwa hoga jisey har padha likha aur un-padh momin padh leyga. uskey fitney mein ye chiz bhi hai ke uskey sath jannat aur jahannam hogi. uski jahannam (haqeeqat mein) jannat hogi aur uski jannat (asal mein) jahannam hogi. jisey uski jahannam ki aazmaaish ka samna karna padey, wo Allah sey fariyad karey aur Sura Kahaf ki ibtidaai aayaat padhey, wo uskey liye thandi aur salamti wali bin jaeygi, jaisey Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) par aag (thandi aur salamti wali) ho gaee thi. uska eik fitna ye bhi hai ke wo eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) sey kaheyga : agar main terey waliden ko zinda kar dun to kya to taslim kar leyga ke main tera Rab hun? wo kaheyga : haan. (fauran) do shetan uskey maa-baap ki surat mein zahir hongey aur usey kahengey : beta ! iski perwi karo, ye tera Rab hai. uska eik aur fitna ye hai ke usey eik insan par qabu diya jaaeyga , wo usey qatl kerega, yani aarey sey cheer dega yahan tak key wo insan do tukdey ho kar gir padeyga, phir wo (doosrey logon sey) kaheyga : merey is bandey ko dekhna, main abhi usey zinda karunga, wo phir bhi yehi kaheyga ke uska merey siwa koi aur Rab hai. Allah Taala us shakhs ko zinda kar dega. khabees (Dajjaal) usey kaheyga : tera Rab kon hai? wo (momin) kaheyga : mera Rab Allah hai aur to Allah ka dushman hai. to Dajjaal hai. Allah ki qism ! terey barey mein jitni samajh mujhey aaj aai hai, pehley nahin aai thi. Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri ummat ka ye aadmi jannat mein sab sey aa'laa maqam par faaiz hoga. Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! hamara to khayal tha ke ye shakhs Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) hi hongey hattaa key wo faut ho gaey. (tab hamein malum huwa ke Dajjaal key haath sey qatl ho kar zinda honey wala, aur phir uski tardeed karney wala shakhs koi aur hoga.) Abu-Raafey (Rahimahullah) apni sanad sey bayan kartey hain ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : uska fitna ye bhi hai ke wo aasman ko barish barsaney ka hukm dega to barish barseygi. aur zamin ko nabatat uganey ka hukm dega to wo ugaeygi. uska fitna ye bhi hai ke wo eik qabiley key paas sey guzreyga, wo uskey da'wey ko taslim nahin kerengey. tab unka koi maweshi nahin bacheyga, sab halak ho jaeyngey. eik aur qabiley key paas sey guzreyga, wo uskey da'wey ko taslim kar leingey. wo aasman ko barish barsaney ka hukm dega to aasman sey barish baras jaeygi. aur zamin ko nabatat uganey ka hukm dega to wo ugaeygi. isi din unkey maweshi Sham ko (char kar) wapis ayengey to bahut motey taazey hongey. un ki kokhein khub phooli hui aur unkey than doodh sey khub bharey huye hongey. wo sari zamin par ghoomeyga aur apna tasallut jamaeyga, siwaye Makka aur Madina key. wo jis darrey sey bhi wahan aayega, aagey sey usey farishtey nangi talwaarein liye milengey yahan tak key wo shor zamin key aakhir mein surkh tiley key paas padaaw daaleyga. tab Madina mein teen baar zalzalaa aayega to har munafiq mard aur munafiq aurat shehar sey nikal kar uskey paas aa jaeyngey. (is tarah) Madiney sey (kufr aur nifaq ki) gandagi is tarah nikal jaeygi jis tarah bhatti lohey ki mail kuchail ko nikal deti hai. wo din najat ka din kehlaaeyga. Hazrat Umme Shareek binte Abu Akar (Raziallahu anha) ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! us waqt ehale Arab kahan hongey? aap ney farmaya is din wo kam hongey. aur taqriban sabhi (Arbi) Baitul-Maqdis mein hongey. unka Imam eik nek aadmi hoga. unka Imam unhein subah ki namaz padhaaney key liye aagey badheyga ke achcha usi subah Hazrat Esa ibne Maryam (Alaihissalam) (zameen par) utar aayengey. unka Imam ultey paon peechhey hatey ga taake Esa (Alaihissalam) logon ko namaz padhaaeyn lekin Hazrat Esa (Alaihissalam) uskey kandhon key darmiyan (kamar par) haath rakh kar usey farmaeyngey : aap hi aagey badh kar namaz padhaein kyonkey iqaamat aap key liye kahi gaee hai, chunanche unka Imam unhein namaz padhaaeyga. jab wo farigh hoga to Esa (Alaihissalam) farmaeyngey : darwaza kholo. darwaza khola jaeyga to aagey Dajjaal mojud hoga. uskey saath sattar hazar Yahudi hongey. har eik key paas muzayyan (saji hui) talwaar aur sabz (hara) chadar hogi. jab Dajjaal aap ko dekhega to is tarah pighlney lagega jaisey namak pani mein pighal jata hai, chunanche wo farar ho jaaeyga. Hazrat Esa (Alaihissalam) farmaeyngey : main tujhey eik zarab lagaaunga, to mujh sey bhag kar us sey bach nahin sakta. aap usey lood shehar key mashriqi darwazey par ja pakdeingey aur qatl kar dengey. tab Allah Taala yahudiyon ko shikast dey dega. Allah ki paida ki hui jis chiz key peechhey bhi koi Yahudi chupeyga us chiz ko Allah bolney ki taqat dey dega, chahey wo koi patthar ho ya darkht, baagh ki deewar ho ya janwer. magar ""gharqad""  jo un (yahudiyon) ka darkht hai, wo nahin boleyga. baqi har chiz kaheygi : aey Allah key musalman bandey ! ye (merey peechhey) Yahudi hai aa kar isey qatl kar dey. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : uski muddat chaalis saal hai. eik saal chhe maah key barabar hoga, eik saal eik mahiney jitna , eik saal eik haftey jitna aur uskey aakhiri din chigaari ki tarah hongey. aadmi subah ko shehar key eik darwazey par hoga aur doosrey darwazey tak pahunchney sey pehley Sham ho jaaeygi. arz kiya gaya Allah key Rasool ! hum un chhotey-chhotey dino mein namazein kis tarah padheingey? aap ney farmaya : jis tarah tum taweel dino mein andazey sey namaz padhtey they, isi tarah un (mukhtasar) dino mein bhi (waqt ka) andaza kar key namazein ada karna. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Esa ibne Maryam (Alaihissalam) meri ummat mein insaf karney waley haakim aur aadil (insaaf pasand) Imam hongey. wo saleeb ko tod dengey, khinzir ko zibeh kar dengey, jiziya khatam kar dengey, sadqa lena band kar dengey, isliye kisi bakri ya oont ki zakat nahin li jaeygi. aapas ki narazi aur dushmani khatam ho jaeygi. zahreeley janweron ka zahar nahin rahega yahan tak key bachcha sanp key munh mein haath dal dega to sanp usey nuqsan nahin pahunchaeyga. aur bachchi sher ko bhagaa degi, wo usey nuqsan nahin pahunchaeyga. bhediya bakriyon mein aisey hoga jaisey rewad ka kutta hota hai. zamin aman sey is tarah bhar jaeygi jaisey bartan pani sey bhar jata hai. sab log muttahid hongey. Allah key siwa kisi ki ibadat nahin ki jaeygi. jang nabud ho jaeygi. Quraish sey hukumat chhin jaeygi. zamin chaandi key thaal ki tarah ho jaeygi. uski pedawar isi tarah hogi jaisey Adam (Alaihissalam) key zamaney mein huwa karti thi yahan tak key kaee afrad mil kar angooron ka eik khosha khaeyn gey to sair ho jaeyngey. aur kaee afrad mil kar eik anaar khaeyn gey to sair ho jaeyngey. eik bail itney itney maal key badley milega, aur eik ghoda chand dirham ka mil jaaeyga. Sahaba Raziallahu anhum ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! ghoda sasta kyon ho jaaeyga? aap ney farmaya is par jang key liye sawari nahin ki jaeygi. unhoney kaha : bail kyon mahngaa hoga? farmaya : sari zamin par kaasht-kaarii hogi. aur Dajjaal key zahir honey sey pehley teen sakht saal ayengey. un mein logon ko sakht bhook ka samna hoga. pehley saal Allah key hukm sey aasman tihai barish rok leyga aur zamin tihai pedawar rok leygi. doosrey saal Allah key hukm sey aasman do tihai barish rok leyga aur zamin do tihai pedawar rok leygi. teesrey saal Allah key hukm sey aasman sari barish rok leyga, eik qatra bhi nahin barseyga. aur zamin sari pedawar rok leygi. koi sabza nahin ugeyga, chunanche sarey maweshi halak ho jaaeyngey magar jo Allah chahey. arz kiya gaya is zamaney mein log kis tarah zinda rahengey? aap ney farmaya : tahleel aur takbir aur tasbih aur tahmeed key zariey sey. ye unkey liye khaney key qaaim maqam ho jaaeygi. Abdur-Rehman Mahaaribi (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain : ye hadees bachchon key ustaad ko deni chahiye ke primary school mein bachchon ko yad karaaey."
4078,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak key Esa ibn Maryam insaf karney waley qazi bin kar aur aadil Imam bin kar nazil hongey. wo saleeb ko tod dengey, jiziya saaqit (khatm) kar dengey aur kasrat sey maal taqseem kerengey yahan tak key koi usey qubul nahin kerega."
4079,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Yajuj Majuj ko khol diya jaeyga, jaisey Allah Taala ney farmaya : ( وَھُمْ مِّنْ کُلِّ حَدَبٍ یَّنْسِلُوْنَ ),''wo har tiley sey bhagtey aayengey.'' to wo sari zamin par phel jaaeyngey. musalman un sey eik taraf ho jaaeyngey (un ki kasrat dekh kar muqabla nahin kerengey) yahan tak key bachey khuchey musalman apney shehron aur qilon mein chaley jaaeyngey aur maweshi bhi apney paas rakhengey (charaagaahon mein nahin chodengey) Yajuj Majuj ka ye haal hoga ke kisi nehar key paas sey guzren-gey to uska sara pani pi jaaeyngey, kuchh nahin chhoden-gey. un ki fauj ka pichhlaa hissa wahan sey guzreyga to un mein sey koi kehney wala kaheyga : (shayad) is jagah kabhi pani hota tha. wo zamin walon par ghalib aa jaaeyngey to un mein sey eik aadmi kaheyga : hum zamin walon sey farigh ho chukey, ab hum aasman walon ka muqabla kerengey. un mein sey jo koi aasman ki taraf apna neza phenkeyga, uska neza khoon-aalood (khoon se ranga) ho kar wapis aayega. tab wo kahengey : hamney aasman walon ko qatl kar diya hai. isi beech mein Allah Taala un par aisey hashraat (keedey-makodey) bhejeyga jaisey tiddi-dal ka laarwaa (eik qisam ka keedaa). wo hashraat (keede-makode) un ki gardanon par hamla-aawar hongey. to wo is tarah mar mar kar eik doosrey par giren-gey jaisey tiddi-dal eik baargi mar jata hai. subah ko musalmanon ko un ki hasa aur harkat sunai na degi to wo kahengey : kon bahaadur aadmi apni jaan khatrey mein dal kar malum karey ke wo kya kar rahey hain? un mein sey eik aadmi (qiley sey) utreyga aur wo (apney dil mein) unkey haathon qatl honey par tayyar hoga, wo dekhega ke sab (Yajuj-Majuj) halak ho chukey hain. wo aawaz dega : khush ho jao ! Allah ney tumharey dushmanon ko tabah kar diya hai. tab (musalman) log (apney hisaar sey) niklengey aur apney janweron ko chhoden gey. janweron ko charney key liye un (Yajuj Majuj) key gosht key siwa koi khurak muyassar na hogi. wo in ko kha-kha kar is tarah motey aur bahut doodh waley ho jaaeyngey jaisey behtareen chaara kha kar khub motey-taazey aur doodh waley ho jatey hain."
4080,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Yajuj-Majuj rozaana (deewar) khodtey hain yahan tak key jab (itni kam moti reh jati hai ke) unhen suraj ki roshni (uskey aar paar) nazar aaney key qarib hoti hai to unka afsar kehta hai : wapis chalo, us (baqi deewar) ko hum kal khod dalengey. Allah Taala usey phir pehley sey bhi intehai sakht kar deta hai. jab unka muqarrar waqt aayega aur Allah Taala ki manshaa hogi ke unhen logon tak pahunchney dey to wo khodengey, jab wo suraj ki roshni dekhney key qarib hongey to unka afsar kaheyga : chalo, is ko hum kal khod leingey Insha-Allah. wo Allah ki marzi ka zikr kerengey to (uski ye barkat hogi ke) jab (subah ko) wapis ayengey to usey usi haalat mein paaeyngey jaisi chhod kar gaey they. wo usey khod kar logon key samney nikal ayengey, aur pani pi kar khatam kar dengey. log un sey bachao key liye qil'a band ho jaeyngey. wo aasman ki taraf teer phenkengey to teer khoon sey tar-bitar wapis aayengey. tab wo kahengey : hamney zamin walon ko zer kar liya aur aasman walon par ghalib aagaey. tab Allah un ki guddhiyon mein keedey paida kar dega jin sey wo halak ho jaaeyngey. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! zamin key janwer unka gosht kha kha kar motey ho jaeyngey aur un par charbi chadh jaaeygi."
4081,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jis raat Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Meraj hui, aap ki mulaqat Hazrat Ibrahim , Hazrat Musa aur Hazrat Iisaa (Alaihissalam) sey bhi hui. wo aapas mein qiyamat key barey mein baat cheet karney lagey. sab sey pehley unhoney Hazrat Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) sey puchha lekin unhein uskey barey mein maloomat nahin thin. phir unhoney Hazrat Musa (Alaihissalam) sey poochha, unhen bhi uska ilm na tha. tab Hazrat Esa ibne Maryam (Alaihissalam) sey baat karney ko kaha gaya to unhoney farmaya : mujhey qiyamat qaaim honey sey pehley ki baaten batai gaee hain, baqi raha uskey qaaim honey ka waqt to wo Allah key siwa kisi ko malum nahin, phir unhoney Dajjaal key zuhoor ka zikr kiya aur farmaya : main nazil ho kar usey qatl karunga, tab log apney apney shehron ko lot jaaeyngey. aagey sey unhen Yajuj Majuj milengey jo har tiley sey tezi key sath utar rahey hongey. wo jis pani (chashmey waghera) key paas sey guzrengey pi jaeyngey. aur jis chiz key paas sey guzren gey, usey kharab kar dengey. tab log Allah sey fariyad kerengey, chunanche main Allah sey dua karunga ke un (Yajuj Majuj) ko tabah kar dey. tab (saari) zamin mein un ki sadaand phel jaaeygi. log Allah sey fariyad kerengey, main bhi Allah sey dua karunga, chunanche Allah Taala aasman sey barish nazil farmaeyga jo unhen utha kar samandar mein phenk degi. phir pahadon ko reza reza kar diya jaeyga aur zamin ko is tarah khinch diya jaeyga jis tarah chamdey ko khinch diya jata hai. mujhey (Esa (Alaihissalam) ko) bataya gaya hai ke jab ye waqiyaa hoga to qiyamat itni qarib hogi jaisey wo hamila jis (ka waqt bilkul qarib ho aur us) key ghar walon ko pata na ho ke kab bchcha wiladat ho jaeygi. (hadees key eik Raavi) Awam bin Hoshab (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : iski taeed Quran Majeed ki is aayat sey bhi hoti hai : ( حَتّٰی اِذجا فُتِحَتْ یَاجُوْجُ وَ مَاجوُج وَھُمْ مِّنْ کُلِّ حَدَبٍ یَّنْسِلُوْنَ ),''yahan tak key jab Yajuj aur Majuj ko khol diya jaaeyga to wo har bulandi sey daudtey huye aayengey.''"
4082,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they ke banu-Hashim key kuchh jawan aagaey. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein dekha to aap ki aakhon mein aansu bhar aaye aur (chehre Mubarak ka) rang tabdeel ho gaya. mainey arz kiya : hamein aap key chehre Mubarak par kuchh aisey aasaar nazar aaye hain jo hamein pasand nahin (hum nahin chahtey ke aap ko ghamgin dekhen). Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hum us gharaney key afrad hain (jinki ye shaan hai ke) Allah ney hamarey liye duniya ki bajaey aakhirat ko pasand farma liya hai. merey ghar walon ko merey baad musibaton, darbadri aur watan sey ikhraaj ka samna karna padeyga yahan tak key mashriq sey kuchh log aayengey unkey paas siyah jhandey hongey. aur wo achchi chiz mangengey to unhen nahin di jaaeygi. phir wo jang kerengey to un ki madad ki jaaeygi (aur Fateh hasil hogi). tab jo kuchh unhoney manga tha unhein pesh kiya jaaeyga lekin wo qubul nahin kerengey yahan tak key wo us (hakumati intizam) ko merey ehal- bait key eik aadmi ko dengey, chunanche wo zamin ko insaf sey is tarah bhar dega jis tarah logon ney isey zulm sey bhar rakha tha. tum mein sey jo un halaat ko paa ley, usey chahiye ke us (Mehdi) key paas aaye agar-che barf par phisal kar aana padey."
4083,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri ummat mein Mehdi hoga. agar (uski muddat) kam hui to saat saal hogi warna no saal. us (key daure-hukoomat) mein meri ummat ko aisi khushiyan milengi jaisi kabhi nahin mili thin. (zameen ko) uskey mewey milen gey. aur wo un (mewon) mein sey kuchh bhi bacha kar nahin rakheygi (puri pedawar degi). un dino maal key ambaar hongey. aadmi uth kar kaheyga : aey Mehdi ! mujhey dijiye aur Mehdi kaheyga : ley ley."
4084,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumharey khazaney key paas teen aadmi aapas mein jang kerengey. un mein sey har eik kisi na kisi khaleefa ka beta hoga. wo khazana un mein sey kisi ko nahin milega. phir mashriq ki taraf sey siyah jhandey zahir hongey aur wo tum logon ko is tarah qatl kerengey ke pehley kisi ney na kiya hoga. phir aap ney kuchh farmaya jo mujhey yad nahin. phir farmaya : jab tum usey dekho to uski baiat karo agar-che barf par ghisat kar aana padey kyonkey wo Allah ka khalifa Mehdi hoga."
4085,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Mehdi hum mein sey, yani ehale bait mein sey hai. Allah usey eik raat mein durust farmaeyga."
4086,"Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyeb (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : hum Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir they ke hamney Mehdi key barey mein baat cheet shuru kar di. Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : Mehdi, Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ki aulad mein sey hoga."
4087,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : hum Abdul-Muttalib ki aulad ehale jannat key sardar hain : main (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)), Hamza , Ali , Jaafar , Hasan , Husain aur Mehdi (Raziallahu anhum)."
4088,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Haris bin Juz Zubaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mashriq sey kuchh log zahir hongey jo Mehdi key liye, yani uski hukumat key liye zamin humwaar karengey."
4089,"Hazrat Khalid bin Maadaan (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Juber bin Nafeer (Rahimahullah) ney mujh sey farmaya : chalo Zu-Mikhmar (Raziallahu anhu) key paas chalen. wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Sahaba they, chunanche (Khalid ney kaha : ) main un (Jubair) key sath chal pada. Juber ney Zu-Mikhmar (Raziallahu anhu) sey jang bandi key mutalliq puchha to unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : anqarib ehale-Rome tum (musalmanon) sey eik pur-aman suleh kerengey. tum aur wo eik (mushtarka) dushman key khilaf jang karogey jis main tum ghalib aaogey. tumhen ghaneematein milengi aur tum salaamat rahogey. phir tum (musalman aur Romi Esai) wapis lotogey hattaa key eik tilon waley murghzaar mein padaaw dalogey. (achanak) saleeb walon mein sey eik aadmi saleeb buland kerega aur (naara lagatey huye) kaheyga : saleeb ghalib aa gaee. eik musalman ghussey hoga aur uth kar saleeb tod dega. us waqt Romi ehad shikni (waada khilaafi) kerengey aur jang key liye jama ho jaaeyngey. Abdur-Rehman bin Ibrahim dimashqi key wastey sey marvi riwayat mein ye izafa hai : wo jang key liye jama ho jaeyngey. tab wo assi jhandon taley (hamley key liye muttahid ho kar) aayengey. har jhandey taley baara hazar (saleebi fauji) hongey."
4090,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab jangein hongi to Allah Taala mawaali (nau muslimon (azaad kiye hue ghulaam)) ka eik lashkar khada kerega. unkey ghodey Arab key behtareen ghodey hongey aur un ke aslaha sab sey umda hongey. Allah Taala unkey zariey sey Deen ki madad kerega."
4091,"Hazrat Nafey bin Utba bin Abu Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum log jazeera Arab walon sey jang karogey, Allah usey Fateh kar dega. phir tum Rome sey jang karogey, Allah usey bhi Fateh kar dega. phir tum Dajjaal sey jang karogey, Allah tumhen is par bhi Fateh dega. Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : Dajjaal zahir nahin hoga jab tak Rome Fateh na ho."
4092,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : badi jang, Qustuntuniya ki Fateh aur Dajjaal ka zuhoor saat maah key andar hoga."
4093,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Basar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jang mein aur shehar (Qustuntuniya) ki Fateh key darmiyan chhe saal ka waqfa hai, aur saatwen saal Dajjaal zahir ho jaaeyga."
4094,"Hazrat Amr bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat nahin aayegi yahan tak key musalmanon key qarib tareen sarhadi muhafiz maqam ""bolaa"" par hongey. phir farmaya : aey Ali ! aey Ali ! aey Ali ! Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kiya : merey maa baap aap par qurban (hazir hun). aap ney farmaya : tum log banu Asfar (Romiyon) sey jang karogey aur tumharey baad waley bhi un sey jang kerengey yahan tak key sab sey afzal musalman, yani Hijaaz waley unkey muqabley key liye niklengey. unhein Allah ki raah mein kisi malamat karney waley ki malamat ka khof nahin hoga. wo Subhan Allah aur Allahu-Akbar key naa,ron sey Qustuntuniya ko Fateh kar leingey. unhein itni ghaneematein milengi jitni pehley kabhi nahin mili thin yahan tak key wo dhaalon key zariey sey taqseem kerengey. (achanak) eik shakhs aa kar kaheyga : tumharey shehron mein Dajjaal zahir ho gaya hai. suno ! ye khabar jhooti hogi. leney wala bhi sharminda hoga aur chhodney wala bhi sharminda hoga."
4095,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumharey darmiyan aur banu Asfar (Romiyon) key darmiyan jang-bandi hogi wo tumhen dhoka dengey aur assi jhandon taley tumhari taraf pesh qadmi kerengey. har jhandey key nichey baara hazar afrad hongey."
4096,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat nahin aayegi yahan tak key tum eik qom sey jang karogey jinkey jootey baalon key hongey. aur qiyamat nahin aayegi yahan tak key tum chhoti aakhon wali eik qom sey jang karogey."
4097,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak key tum aisey logon sey jang karogey jinki aankhen chhoti aur naakein chapti hain. unkey chehrey aisey hain jaisey teh-daar dhaaleyn. aur qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak key tum un logon sey jang karogey jinkey jootey baalon key hain."
4098,"Hazrat Amr bin Taghlab Namri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna, aap farma rahey they : qiyamat ki eik nishani ye bhi hai ke tum chaudey chehrey walon sey jang karogey. unkey chehrey goya teh-daar dhaaleyn hain. aur qiyamat ki eik nishani ye bhi hai ke tum un logon sey jang karogey jo baalon key jootey pehantey hain."
4099,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat nahin aayegi yahan tak key tum aisi qom sey jang karogey jinki aankhen chhoti aur chehrey chaudey hongey. un ki aankhen aisi hongi jaisey tiddiyon ki aankhen. aur unkey chehrey aisey hongey jaisey teh-daar dhaaleyn. baalon key jootey pehantey hongey aur chamdey ki dhaaleyn istimal kerengey. wo apney ghodey khajoor key darakhton sey baandhengey."
